cept trades and have competitive financing available. Call today for more information. Options Equipped on Vessel: Twin Yanmar 320hp Diesel Engines, Straight Shaft Bow & Stern Thrusters Essential Trim Package Marlin White Exterior Upholstery Upgraded Electronics Package Marlin White Salon Upholstery Additional Anchor Fitting Anchoring/Mooring Package Flybridge Bimini Top Foredeck Sun Pad Underwater Lights Flybridge Grill Tropical Air Conditioning System 6 Person China Set Low Maintenance White Hull Slatted Cabinet Doors Inverter Rear Facing Camera Radar Automatic Fire Suppression System Mosquito Screen System The Swift Trawler 41 successfully renews the spirit and style of the trawler range. Ample living space, comfortable and practical, this innovative 40-foot powerboat, available in both Fly and Sedan versions, has an on-board capacity of up to 7 passengers. The Swift Trawler 41 has a fluid and balanced profile, emphasized by a slender flared out hull, which means she cuts perfectly through the sea. Her wheelhouse offers a strikingly generous glazed space, while the fore deck, with its large sun pad and a high protective pulpit make this long-distance cruiser even more distinctive. Her hull has also been designed for optimum fuel consump…', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/90/88/2026-beneteau-swift-trawler-41-fly-power-9729088-20260225131411629-3.jpg?w=1920&h=267&t=1772054954000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/90/88/2026-beneteau-swift-trawler-41-fly-power-9729088-20260225131401602-1.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1772054944000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/90/88/2026-beneteau-swift-trawler-41-fly-power-9729088-20260225131402561-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1772054945000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/90/88/2026-beneteau-swift-trawler-41-fly-power-9729088-20260225131403474-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1772054946000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/90/88/2026-beneteau-swift-trawler-41-fly-power-9729088-20260225131404279-4.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1772054946000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/90/88/2026-beneteau-swift-trawler-41-fly-power-9729088-20260225131410008-1.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1772054952000&exact=&format=webp"]', 'Boat DetailsDescriptionAvailable now for immediate delivery, factory fresh 2026. Well optioned for completing America''s Great Loop or cruising. Our pricing includes dingy & motor, Hurley H30 dingy davit, SeaHawk Cukote bottom paint, Propspeed, all required USCG safety equipment, basic boating gear, on-water training, Smart TVs, and complementary wet slippage. We are the Swift Trawler outfitter specialist. We can install Starlink, SeaKeeeper, Window Tint, Water Maker, Snuba System, Custom Upholstery and much more. Let us outfit your dream Swift Trawler! We accept trades and have competitive financing available. Call today for more information. Options Equipped on Vessel: Twin Yanmar 320hp Diesel Engines, Straight Shaft Bow & Stern Thrusters Essential Trim Package Marlin White Exterior Upholstery Upgraded Electronics Package Marlin White Salon Upholstery Additional Anchor Fitting Anchoring/Mooring Package Flybridge Bimini Top Foredeck Sun Pad Underwater Lights Flybridge Grill Tropical Air Conditioning System 6 Person China Set Low Maintenance White Hull Slatted Cabinet Doors Inverter Rear Facing Camera Radar Automatic Fire Suppression System Mosquito Screen System The Swift Trawler 41 successfully renews the spirit and style of the trawler range. Ample living space, comfortable and practical, this innovative 40-foot powerboat, available in both Fly and Sedan versions, has an on-board capacity of up to 7 passengers. The Swift Trawler 41 has a fluid and balanced profile, emphasized by a slender flared out hull, which means she cuts perfectly through the sea. Her wheelhouse offers a strikingly generous glazed space, while the fore deck, with its large sun pad and a high protective pulpit make this long-distance cruiser even more distinctive. Her hull has also been designed f…', '2026-04-01T18:18:31.190Z', '2026-04-01T18:18:31.190Z', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Please contact Leo Page at 407-394-7623', 'Leo Page', '407-394-7623', 'DisclaimerThe Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors, to investigate such details as the buyer desires validated. This vessel is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal without notice.', 'The Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors, to investigate such details as the buyer desires validated. This vessel is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal without notice.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Engine 1Engine Make:YanmarEngine Model:8LV320Total Power:320hpEngine Type:InboardDrive Type:Direct DriveFuel Type:DieselEngine 2Engine Make:YanmarEngine Model:8LV320Total Power:320hpEngine Type:InboardDrive Type:Direct DriveFuel Type:Diesel', 'Yanmar', '8LV320', NULL, '320hp', NULL, 'Inboard', 'Direct Drive', 'Diesel', NULL, NULL, 'DimensionsLength Overall:44.08ftMax Draft:3.75ftBeam:13.92ftWeightsDry Weight:24,332LbMiscellaneousHull Material:FiberglassTanksFresh Water Tank:106 gal Fuel Tank:309 gal Holding Tank:AccommodationsGuest Cabins:3Guest Heads:2', NULL, NULL, NULL, '44.08ft', NULL, '3.75ft', NULL, '13.92ft', '24,332Lb', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Fiberglass', NULL, NULL, '106 gal', '309 gal', NULL, '2', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/90/88/2026-beneteau-swift-trawler-41-fly-power-9729088-20260225131411629-3.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1772054954000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup