 NULL, 'Please contact Drew Baldwin at 954-527-4848', 'Drew Baldwin', '954-527-4848', 'DescriptionMain Salon Accessed through curved sliding glass doors from the aft deck, the salon is arranged for both entertaining and day-to-day comfort. The space features high-gloss cherry cabinetry, large side windows with Roman shades, and a formal dining area forward. • Two leather sofas• Cherry cabinetry with storage throughout• Cherry and glass coffee table• Formal dining table for six• Integrated surround sound system• Cruisair SMX climate controls• Staircase access to bridge A day head is located to starboard just aft of the pilothouse, finished with marble sole and vanity, VacuFlush head, and mirrored accents. Master Stateroom The full-beam master suite is located amidships for optimal comfort underway. The layout provides generous storage and seating in addition to the centerline queen berth. • Queen berth with built-in nightstands• Curved leather settee• Walk-in wardrobe• Vanity with seating• Entertainment system• Portholes with shades Master Ensuite • Marble countertops and flooring• Dual sinks with storage below• VacuFlush toilet and bidet• Enclosed shower with bi-fold doors VIP Stateroom Forward VIP with centerline queen berth and private head. • Queen berth with nigh…', 'The Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors, to investigate such details as the buyer desires validated. This vessel is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal without notice.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Engine 1Engine Make:MTUEngine Model:12V 2000 M 90Engine Year:1999Total Power:1350hpEngine Hours:3300Engine Type:InboardFuel Type:DieselEngine 2Engine Make:MTUEngine Model:12V 2000 M 90Engine Year:1999Total Power:1350hpEngine Hours:3300Engine Type:InboardFuel Type:Diesel', 'MTU', '12V 2000 M 90', '1