 cruising and entertaining without the worry of maintaining Stern Drives. The wide set twin outboard design and bow thruster make docking a dream. The innovative design creates a larger cockpit, stowage and cabin space. Head, Refrigerator, Air Conditioning, large dining table and galley in the cabin and a grill, wet bar, and refrigerator and dining table on the Party Deck, Family and Friends will enjoy the Sun with new cushions on the Bow and will stay cool under the extra-large Bimini with shade for the entire afternoon seating area. This is the Cruiser to let you explore the Sand Bars from Boca, Fort Lauderdale, Miami, Key Biscayne and the rest of the Florida Keys. Kohler 5Kw Generator 126 hours New Custom Cushions Feb 2024 New Windlass Motor Jan 2024 Decking Refinished Jan 2024 Key Features: Outboard Engine Propulsion Standard air conditioning/heating. Enclosed head with VacuFlush® head system. Full Beam, mid-master stateroom with double berth & sofa SmartCraft® instrumentation standard.', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/92/49/2014-sea-ray-370-venture-power-10089249-20260220092712363-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1771609335000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/92/49/2014-sea-ray-370-venture-power-10089249-20260220092844715-1.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1771609427000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/92/49/2014-sea-ray-370-venture-power-10089249-20260220093213266-1.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1771609642000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/92/49/2014-sea-ray-370-venture-power-10089249-20260220093214313-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1771609648000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/92/49/2014-sea-ray-370-venture-power-10089249-20260220093215294-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1771609645000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/92/49/2014-sea-ray-370-venture-power-10089249-20260220093216302-4.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1771