ahead of its time and ready for serious fishing. The deck features dual aquarium livewells, a large bow casting deck with lockable rod storage, plenty of comfortable seating for up to 10 people, best-in-class bilge access, and much more. All of this is paired with a very capable hull designed for shallow water and a smooth ride. The Masters 247 now features the revolutionary Seakeeper Ride System in a first-of-its-kind built-in pocket design. This system uses actuators and stabilization technology to improve the ride quality in any condition, providing a smoother and more comfortable ride for all onboard. The Seakeeper Ride system is seamlessly integrated into the boat''s transom design, making it virtually invisible. With this cutting-edge feature, the Masters 247 sets a new standard for bay boats and offers a level of comfort and stability that was previously unheard of in its class. Included Options • Trolling Motor Package • 2 x 10'' Power Pole Blades on JP Bracket • Forward seating package with back rest • Bottom Paint (Black) Manufacturer Options • Seakeeper Ride System – automated ride leveling system • Jack plate • Hull side – White / Hull bottom – White • Fiberglass console with FG liner & 7 gal livewell • Fiberglass hardtop with LED lighti…', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/66/69/2024-sportsman-masters-247-bay-boat-power-10116669-20260321152412762-1.jpg?w=1920&h=267&t=1774804151000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/66/69/2024-sportsman-masters-247-bay-boat-power-10116669-20260321152413494-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774804151000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/66/69/2024-sportsman-masters-247-bay-boat-power-10116669-20260321152414186-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774804151000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/66/69/2024-sportsman-masters-247-bay-boat-power-10116669-20260321152414840-4.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774804151000&exact=&format=webp","ht