System – automated ride leveling system • Jack plate • Hull side – White / Hull bottom – White • Fiberglass console with FG liner & 7 gal livewell • Fiberglass…', '2026-04-01T18:18:42.966Z', '2026-04-01T18:18:42.966Z', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Please contact Michael Hawkins at 904-631-3547', 'Michael Hawkins', '904-631-3547', 'Electronics, Console and Helm SportLink® Electronics Integration System Compass Dash Panel Cover Dual Battery Configuration w/ Switch & Trays Fiberglass Hard-Top w/ Integrated D-Tubing Frame Garmin Apollo™ RA670 Premium Stereo w/ SportTuun Garmin GPSMAP® 1243xsv MFD 12" w/ Bluechart G3 Garmin GT12M 350w CHIRP Bronze Thru-Hull Transducer Garmin VHF 115 Radio w/ Antenna Garmin XS Series Marine Speakers w/ White Sport Grilles (8) Horn Hydraulic Tilt Steering Integrated Hard-Top Navigation Lights (Lumitec) Integrated Tempered Glass Windshield w/ Vent Interior LED Lighting Package King Fish Rod Holders Lockable Console Storage Maretron MPower® Digital Switching w/ Keypad Matching Hard-Top Underside Color Seakeeper Ride VACS Trolling Motor Plug & Harness Underwater Lights USB Audio Plug In-Dash & 12V Receptacle Seating, Upholstery and Pads Cockpit Bolsters Console Footrest w/ Storage & Pads Helm Pad Premium Dual Chair LP w/ Flip Up Bolsters & Armrests Premium Sileather® Marine Silicone Fabrics Rear Fold Up Bench Seat w/ Storage Under Gunwale Reel Pads Livewells, Pumps and Storage (1) 25 Gallon Aquarium Rear Livewell (1) 25 Gallon Aquarium Rear Recirculating Livewell w/Pro-Air 13 Gallon F…', 'The Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors, to investigate such details as the buyer desires validated. This vessel is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal without notice.', 'Electrical EquipmentShore Power Inlet:✓Inside Equipmentseakeeper:✓Electric Bilge Pump:✓Manual