 with outboards, designed to maximize cockpit space, seating, and social areas while still delivering the performance of a true sport boat. Regal’s thoughtful layout makes this boat perfect for sandbar days, cruising, entertaining guests, and family watersports. Inside the spacious cockpit you’ll find comfortable wraparound seating, a cockpit table for entertaining, and a Garmin multifunction display at the helm for navigation and system monitoring. The layout of the 29 OBX is designed for luxury day boating, entertaining, and relaxed cruising, making it a standout in the premium outboard bowrider category. Key Features & Highlights Twin Yamaha 250 HP Four-Stroke Outboards – Approx. 555 Hours Bow Thruster for Easy Docking and Maneuvering Power Tower Folding Arch Garmin Multifunction Display Spacious Cockpit with Cockpit Table Premium Bowrider Layout with Extensive Seating Graphite Hull Sides with White Boot Stripe Luxury Day Boat Perfect for Cruising and Entertaining Trailer Included The Regal 29 OBX is known for its smooth ride, premium build quality, and innovative layout, making it one of the most desirable large outboard-powered bowriders on the market. Whether you’re hosting friends at the sandbar, cruis…', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/63/86/2019-regal-29-obx-power-10106386-20260310185852823-1.jpg?w=1920&h=267&t=1773195235000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/63/86/2019-regal-29-obx-power-10106386-20260310185841937-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1773195224000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/63/86/2019-regal-29-obx-power-10106386-20260310185842817-4.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1773195225000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/63/86/2019-regal-29-obx-power-10106386-20260310185910371-4.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1773195253000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/63/86/2019-regal-29-obx-power-10106386-20260310185923298-1.jpg?w=1920&ratio=