d SeaV2 hull. Key Features Discover Luxury on Water - Introducing the 2026 Grady-White Freedom 275, a masterpiece of luxury and adventure. This stunning vessel is designed for those who appreciate the finer things in life, boasting exquisite craftsmanship and top-tier performance for unforgettable experiences on the open water. Performance and Power - Equipped with a single, robust engine, the Freedom 275 promises an exhilarating ride, providing the excitement that only Grady-White can deliver. Experience a perfect balance of agility and stability, making every journey not just a trip, but an adventure to cherish. Luxurious Interior - The interior of this model envelops you in comfort, with plush seating and state-of-the-art amenities to ensure a relaxing voyage. Whether you''re fishing with friends or cruising with family, the Freedom 275 is designed for maximum enjoyment.', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/66/49/2026-grady-white-freedom-275-power-9996649-20251030100410017-0.jpg?w=1920&h=267&t=1774879656000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/66/49/2026-grady-white-freedom-275-power-9996649-20251030100410028-1.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774879657000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/66/49/2026-grady-white-freedom-275-power-9996649-20251030100410038-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774879657000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/66/49/2026-grady-white-freedom-275-power-9996649-20251030100410049-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774879657000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/66/49/2026-grady-white-freedom-275-power-9996649-20251030100410059-4.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774879657000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/66/49/2026-grady-white-freedom-275-power-9996649-20251030100410068-5.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774879657000&exact=&format=webp"]', 'Boat DetailsDescription Just landed and ready to make waves! For fishing, w