ore capability, and incredibly smooth low-speed maneuverability thanks to Mercury’s integrated electric steering and joystick piloting. The addition of the Seakeeper dramatically reduces roll at anchor and underway, making every outing more comfortable for owners and guests alike. Performance & Handling Twin Mercury 600HP V12 Verado outboards Joystick piloting with Skyhook® digital anchoring Seakeeper gyro stabilizer Autopilot Advanced helm electronics package Exceptional cruising efficiency and offshore performance This is a true sport yacht with the versatility of outboard power and the ride quality Cruisers Yachts is known for. Entertaining & Deck Layout The 42 GLS was designed as the ultimate luxury day yacht and weekend cruiser. Port & Starboard fold-down beach doors expanding cockpit space Expansive convertible aft seating Premium hardtop with retractable sunroof hardtop Outdoor galley with grill, refrigeration, and sink Upgraded Rockford Fosgate sound system Ownership & Maintenance This vessel has been professionally maintained since new, with routine service performed and systems cared for proactively. She presents exceptionally well and is turnkey for her next owner. If you are searching for a late-model, fully optioned…', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/82/96/2023-cruisers-yachts-42-gls-ob-power-10088296-20260219140642979-1.jpg?w=1920&h=267&t=1771539705000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/82/96/2023-cruisers-yachts-42-gls-ob-power-10088296-20260219140637354-4.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1771539701000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/82/96/2023-cruisers-yachts-42-gls-ob-power-10088296-20260219140637081-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1771539699000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/82/96/2023-cruisers-yachts-42-gls-ob-power-10088296-20260219140636789-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1771539699000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/82/9