ctively. She presents exceptionally well and is turnkey for her next owner. If you are searching for a lat…', '2026-04-01T18:10:54.711Z', '2026-04-01T18:10:54.711Z', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Please contact Matt Jobe at 918-527-0021', 'Matt Jobe', '918-527-0021', 'DisclaimerThe Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors, to investigate such details as the buyer desires validated. This vessel is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal without notice.', 'The Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors, to investigate such details as the buyer desires validated. This vessel is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal without notice.', 'Electrical EquipmentShore Power Inlet:✓Generator:✓ElectronicsDepthsounder:✓Radar:✓Log-Speedometer:✓Navigation Center:✓Plotter:✓DVD Player:✓Autopilot:✓Radio:✓Compass:✓GPS:✓Cockpit Speakers:✓Flat Screen TV:✓AIS:✓Inside Equipmentseakeeper:✓Electric Bilge Pump:✓Microwave Oven:✓Air Conditioning:✓Electric Head:✓Heating:✓Hot Water:✓Refrigerator:✓Deep Freezer:✓Battery Charger:✓', 'Shore Power Inlet | Generator', 'Depthsounder | Radar | Log-Speedometer | Navigation Center | Plotter | DVD Player | Autopilot | Radio | Compass | GPS | Cockpit Speakers | Flat Screen TV | AIS', 'seakeeper | Electric Bilge Pump | Microwave Oven | Air Conditioning | Electric Head | Heating | Hot Water | Refrigerator | Deep Freezer | Battery Charger', NULL, NULL, 'Engine 1Engine Make:MercuryEngine Model:VeradoTotal Power:600hpEngine Hours:75Engine Type:OutboardFuel Type:GasEngine 2Engine Make:MercuryEngine Model:VeradoTotal Power:600hpEngine Hours:72Engine Type:OutboardFuel Type:Gas', 'Mercury', 'Ve