ign The Sea Ray 47 Sedan Bridge remains one of the most desirable yachts in her class due…', '2026-04-01T18:10:49.910Z', '2026-04-01T18:10:49.910Z', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Please contact Matt Jobe at 918-527-0021', 'Matt Jobe', '918-527-0021', 'DisclaimerThe Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors, to investigate such details as the buyer desires validated. This vessel is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal without notice.', 'The Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors, to investigate such details as the buyer desires validated. This vessel is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal without notice.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Engine 1Engine Make:CumminsEngine Model:QSC8.3-600 HOTotal Power:600hpEngine Hours:512Engine Type:InboardFuel Type:DieselEngine 2Engine Make:CumminsEngine Model:QSC8.3-600 HOTotal Power:600hpEngine Hours:512Engine Type:InboardFuel Type:Diesel', 'Cummins', 'QSC8.3-600 HO', NULL, '600hp', '512', 'Inboard', NULL, 'Diesel', NULL, NULL, 'DimensionsLength Overall:50.67ftMax Draft:4.17ftBeam:14.67ftWeightsDry Weight:37,500LbMiscellaneousDeadrise At Transom:19degHull Material:FiberglassHull Shape:Semi-DisplacementTanksFresh Water Tank:117 gal Fuel Tank:530 gal Holding Tank:60 gal AccommodationsGuest Heads:2', NULL, NULL, NULL, '50.67ft', NULL, '4.17ft', NULL, '14.67ft', '37,500Lb', NULL, NULL, '19deg', 'Fiberglass', 'Semi-Displacement', NULL, '117 gal', '530 gal', '60 gal', '2', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/80/21/2009-sea-ray-47-sedan-bridge-power-10078021-20260212125829702-1.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1770930873000&exact&format=webp","https: