er-10131888-20260329154128576-1.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1774887313000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/18/88/1999-viking-58-convertible-power-10131888-20260329154118828-3.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1774887313000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/18/88/1999-viking-58-convertible-power-10131888-20260329154123015-4.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1774887313000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/18/88/1999-viking-58-convertible-power-10131888-20260329154129766-3.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1774887313000&exact&format=webp"]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Freeport, Texas, US', 'Freeport', 'Texas', 'US', NULL, NULL, 'city', 'apple', NULL, 'Freeport, Texas, US', NULL, '2026-03-31T21:01:06.754Z', 1, 0);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO boats (id, listing_id, source, url, make, model, year, length, price, currency, location, city, state, country, description, seller_type, listing_type, images, full_text, scraped_at, updated_at, search_length_min, search_length_max, search_type, search_location, contact_info, contact_name, contact_phone, other_details, disclaimer, features, electrical_equipment, electronics, inside_equipment, outside_equipment, additional_equipment, propulsion, engine_make, engine_model, engine_year_detail, total_power, engine_hours, engine_type_detail, drive_type, fuel_type_detail, propeller_type, propeller_material, specifications, cruising_speed, max_speed, range, length_overall, max_bridge_clearance, max_draft, min_draft_detail, beam_detail, dry_weight, windlass, electrical_circuit, deadrise_at_transom, hull_material, hull_shape, keel_type, fresh_water_tank, fuel_tank, holding_tank, guest_heads, source_images, entity_id, superseded_by_boat_id, dedupe_method, dedupe_confidence, normalized_location, normalized_city, normalized_state, normalized_country, geo_lat, geo_lng, geo_precision, geo_provider, geo_status, geo_query, geo_error, geo_updated_at, geo_normalization_version, needs_rescrape) VALUES (10235, '10121697', 'YachtWorld', 'https://www.yachtworld.com/yacht/2000-maxum-3700-scr-10121697/', 'Maxum', '3700 SCR', 2000, '40ft', '120000', 'USD', 'Long Beach, California', 'Long Beach', 'California', 'US', '2000 Maxum 3700 SCR — Twin Cummins Diesels (Be sure to watch the YouTube Video!!) Powered by twin Cummins 6BTA 5.9 diesels—rare and highly sought after in a vessel of this size—this 2000 Maxum 3700 SCR stands apart from the typical gas-powered express cruisers on the market today. With an overall length just under 40 feet, she delivers the space, presence, and ride of a larger yacht in a highly versatile and manageable package—further enhanced by a premium, fully upgraded JL Audio sound system that sets the tone the moment you step aboard. Performance & Ride Her deep-V hull and diesel inboard configuration provide a smooth, confident ride with efficient performance across a wide range of cruising speeds. She cruises comfortably in the low-20 knot range with top speeds approaching 30 knots, depending on load and conditions. Vee drives offer durability and simplicity, well suited for Southern California coastal cruising and Catalina runs. Cockpit & Deck The cockpit is designed with entertaining in mind, featuring generous seating, a wet bar, and a layout that naturally brings people together. Easy access from the swim platform leads forward to a well-organized helm with excellent visibility and intuitive controls. A portside companion seat keeps guests engaged underway, while the forward sunpad offers a comfortable place to relax on the water. Interior Accommodations Below deck, the 13’1” beam translates into a surprisingly spacious interior. The salon features comfortable seating with convertible sleeping accommodations, complemented by a functional galley positioned for convenience. Forward, the island berth provides a private retreat, while the mid-cabin offers additional sleeping space for guests. The settee easily converts to an additional berth for additional guests…', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/16/97/2000-maxum-3700-scr-power-10121697-20260321092447666-1.jpg?w=1920&h=267&t=1774111189000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/16/97/2000-maxum-3700-scr-power-10121697-20260320092818307-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774030261000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/16/97/2000-maxum-3700-scr-power-10121697-20260320092818485-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774030261000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/16/97/2000-maxum-3700-scr-power-10121697-20260329181754309-1.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774834382000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/16/97/2000-maxum-3700-scr-power-10121697-20260320092820037-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774033953000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/16/97/2000-maxum-3700-scr-power-10121697-20260320092820271-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774033953000&exact=&format=webp"]', 'Boat DetailsDescription2000 Maxum 3700 SCR — Twin Cummins Diesels (Be sure to watch the YouTube Video!!) Powered by twin Cummins 6BTA 5.9 diesels—rare and highly sought after in a vessel of this size—this 2000 Maxum 3700 SCR stands apart from the typical gas-powered express cruisers on the market today. With an overall length just under 40 feet, she delivers the space, presence, and ride of a larger yacht in a highly versatile and manageable package—further enhanced by a premium, fully upgraded JL Audio sound system that sets the tone the moment you step aboard. Performance & Ride Her deep-V hull and diesel inboard configuration provide a smooth, confident ride with efficient performance across a wide range of cruising speeds. She cruises comfortably in the low-20 knot range with top speeds approaching 30 knots, depending on load and conditions. Vee drives offer durability and simplicity, well suited for Southern California coastal cruising and Catalina runs. Cockpit & Deck The cockpit is designed with entertaining in mind, featuring generous seating, a wet bar, and a layout that naturally brings people together. Easy access from the swim platform leads forward to a well-organized helm with excellent visibility and intuitive controls. A portside companion seat keeps guests engaged underway, while the forward sunpad offers a comfortable place to relax on the water. Interior Accommodations Below deck, the 13’1” beam translates into a surprisingly spacious interior. The salon features comfortable seating with convertible sleeping accommodations, complemented by a functional galley positioned for convenience. Forward, the island berth provides a private retreat, while the mid-cabin offers additional sleeping space for guests. The settee easily converts to an additional bert…', '2026-04-01T18:17:24.341Z', '2026-04-01T18:17:24.341Z', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Please contact Steven Henry at 310-547-4415', 'Steven Henry', '310-547-4415', 'TURN IT UP!!A music lovers dream system! This is not your typical marine stereo. Built around a Fusion MS-RA770 head unit and a premium JL Audio system, it delivers powerful, crystal-clear sound with deep bass and full coverage throughout the boat—an audio experience rarely found in this class. System Details Fusion MS-RA770 head unit (6) JL Audio M6 7.7” speakers (2) JL Audio M6 10” subwoofers (4) Fusion 6.5” speakers (2) JL Audio 8.8” tower speakers Additional subwoofer (tube) under galley settee JL Audio 6/600 amplifier JL Audio 700/5 amplifier JL Audio 600W mono amplifier Northern Lights 9KW Generator/Electrical A Northern Lights generator was installed in 2020 (approx. 1,488 hours). In 2025, the generator’s electrical end (power generation side) was replaced, representing a significant recent upgrade to the system. New Xantrex 3000 watt Inverter 2024 New Promarine Battery Charger 2024 New House Batteries 4-6 volt 07/24 New Grp 31 starting Bateries 11/24 @ L6 volts stereo system batteries 11/24 Maintenance Owner has maintained the vessel to the highest standards by Pacific Marine Service. Consistent yearly oil changes and cooling system flushes and general maintenance eg. Hoses…', 'The Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors, to investigate such details as the buyer desires validated. This vessel is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal without notice.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Engine 1Engine Make:CumminsEngine Model:6BTA 5.9Total Power:330hpEngine Hours:2008Engine Type:InboardDrive Type:V-driveFuel Type:DieselPropeller Type:4 BladePropeller Material:BronzeEngine 2Engine Make:CumminsEngine Model:6BTA 5.9Total Power:330hpEngine Hours:1995Engine Type:InboardDrive Type:V-driveFuel Type:DieselPropeller Type:4 BladePropeller Material:Bronze', 'Cummins', '6BTA 5.9', NULL, '330hp', '2008 | 1995', 'Inboard', 'V-drive', 'Diesel', '4 Blade', 'Bronze', 'Speed & DistanceCruising Speed:22knMax Speed:30knDimensionsLength Overall:39.83ftMin Draft:3.08ftBeam:13.08ftLength at Waterline:37ftMiscellaneousWindlass:Electric WindlassDeadrise At Transom:18degHull Material:FiberglassHull Shape:Deep VeeTanksFresh Water Tank:1 x 70 gal Fuel Tank:2 x 300 gal Holding Tank:1 x 40 gal AccommodationsGuest Cabins:2Guest Heads:1', '22kn', '30kn', NULL, '39.83ft', NULL, NULL, '3.08ft', '13.08ftLength at Waterline:37ft', NULL, 'Electric Windlass', NULL, '18deg', 'Fiberglass', 'Deep Vee', NULL, '1 x 70 gal', '2 x 300 gal', '1 x 40 gal', '1', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/16/97/2000-maxum-3700-scr-power-10121697-20260321092447666-1.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1774111189000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/16/97/2000-maxum-3700-scr-power-10121697-20260320092818307-2.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1774030261000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/16/97/2000-maxum-3700-scr-power-10121697-20260320092818485-3.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1774030261000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/16/97/2000-maxum-3700-scr-power-10121697-20260329181754309-1.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1774834382000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/16/97/2000-maxum-3700-scr-power-10121697-20260320092820037-2.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1774033953000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/16/97/2000-maxum-3700-scr-power-10121697-20260320092820271-3.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1774033953000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/16/97/2000-maxum-3700-scr-power-10121697-20260320092820485-4.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1774033953000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/16/97/2000-maxum-3700-scr-power-10121697-20260320092821498-1.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1774033953000&exact&format=webp"]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Long Beach, California, US', 'Long Beach', 'California', 'US', 33.7692853, -118.1863388, 'city', 'apple', 'matched', 'Long Beach, California, US', NULL, '2026-04-01T18:17:24.341Z', 1, 0);
