ow-Thruster, Water-Maker, Dinghy with Electric Davit on Bow, Air-Conditioning & Heating, Upper Helm, Inside Helm & Cockpit Controls. The accommodation features two cozy cabins and a well-appointed head, providing comfort for overnight trips. Equipped with an electric windlass, this boat enhances convenience during anchoring. With 900 hours on the engines, "I''m Broke" is ready for new adventures, combining functionality with the thrill of saltwater fishing. Experience the joy of the open sea with this remarkable vessel, perfect for both seasoned anglers and those seeking relaxation on the water.', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/30/50/2003-mediterranean-38-convertible-power-9763050-20250813135012082-1.jpg?w=1920&h=267&t=1755119114000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/30/50/2003-mediterranean-38-convertible-power-9763050-20250813134940576-4.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1755119084000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/30/50/2003-mediterranean-38-convertible-power-9763050-20250813135005990-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1755119108000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/30/50/2003-mediterranean-38-convertible-power-9763050-20250813134954360-4.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1755119097000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/30/50/2003-mediterranean-38-convertible-power-9763050-20250813134953598-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1755119096000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/30/50/2003-mediterranean-38-convertible-power-9763050-20250813135012844-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1755119115000&exact=&format=webp"]', 'Boat DetailsDescriptionIntroducing the Mediterranean 38 Convertible, a stunning saltwater fishing vessel from 2003, measuring an impressive 43.5 feet in overall length. This used boat boasts a robust fiberglass hull with a modified vee shape, ensuring stability and performance on the water. Powered by twin Volvo TAMD73P-EDC inboard engines, each delivering 430 horsepower, it offers a cruising speed of 22 knots and a maximum hull speed of 25 knots, making it an excellent choice for both fishing and leisurely cruising. Loaded with great features such as, Bow-Thruster, Water-Maker, Dinghy with Electric Davit on Bow, Air-Conditioning & Heating, Upper Helm, Inside Helm & Cockpit Controls. The accommodation features two cozy cabins and a well-appointed head, providing comfort for overnight trips. Equipped with an electric windlass, this boat enhances convenience during anchoring. With 900 hours on the engines, "I''m Broke" is ready for new adventures, combining functionality with the thrill of saltwater fishing. Experience the joy of the open sea with this remarkable vessel, perfect for both seasoned anglers and those seeking relaxation on the water.Show MoreContact InformationPlease contact Capt. Tim Hagan at 714.926.6775Other DetailsEngines Twin Diesel Inboards Volvo Model-TAMD73P-EDC Port Serial Number-2071132775 Starboard Serial Number-2071134632 430hp. Each Engine Batteries West Marine May 2/24 Two burner Princess stove top Ice Maker in galley DisclaimerThe Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors, to investigate such details as the buyer desires validated. This vessel is offered subject to prior sale…', '2026-04-01T18:06:20.046Z', '2026-04-01T18:06:20.046Z', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Please contact Capt. Tim Hagan at 714.926.6775', 'Capt. Tim Hagan', '714.926.6775', 'Engines Twin Diesel Inboards Volvo Model-TAMD73P-EDC Port Serial Number-2071132775 Starboard Serial Number-2071134632 430hp. Each Engine Batteries West Marine May 2/24 Two burner Princess stove top Ice Maker in galley DisclaimerThe Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor w