 cruises in the low 30s. Docking is made easy thanks to a bow thruster, and the large cockpit offers ample seating for entertaining, complete with underwater lights for added flair at night. Down below, the cabin sleeps four with a forward convertible berth and a spacious aft stateroom. The full galley and enclosed head provide all the comforts of home. Garmin electronics are at the helm, and the owners recently completed a full detail—this boat is clean, well-equipped, and ready to enjoy. Contact the listing agent by phone, text, or email for more information or to schedule a showing. Notable Features: • Full set of Garmin electronics including chartplotters and VHF • Kohler generator • Reverse cycle air-conditioning and heating • Underwater lights • Bow thruster • Electric retractable arch for towing or low bridge clearance • Fresh water flush ports for engines • Recent exterior wax detailShow MoreContact InformationPlease contact Tom Hugh-Jones at (310) 658-0700Other DetailsDisclaimerDenison Yacht Sales offers the details of this yacht in good faith but can’t guarantee the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of this boat for sale. This yacht for sale is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal from that yacht market without notice. She is offered as a convenience by this yacht broker to its clients and is not intended to convey direct representation of a specific yacht for sale. Need more details?Ask the…', '2026-04-01T18:00:05.103Z', '2026-04-01T18:00:05.103Z', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Please contact Tom Hugh-Jones at (310) 658-0700', 'Tom Hugh-Jones', '(310) 658-0700', 'DisclaimerDenison Yacht Sales offers the details of this yacht in good faith but can’t guarantee the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of this boat for sale. This yacht for sale is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal from that yacht market without notice. She is offered as a convenience by this yacht broker to its c