e for relaxation and privacy. The electric windlass enhances convenience during anchoring, making your adventures even more enjoyable. Whether you''re exploring coastal waters or embarking on longer journeys, the Panaseaya is equipped to meet your needs with style and reliability. Experience the perfect blend of luxury and performance with this remarkable vessel, ready to create unforgettable memories on the water.', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/92/75/1986-hi-star-aft-cabin-power-10069275-20260129224002843-1.jpg?w=1920&h=267&t=1773118887000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/92/75/1986-hi-star-aft-cabin-power-10069275-20260129224003212-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774980543000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/92/75/1986-hi-star-aft-cabin-power-10069275-20260129224003413-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774980543000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/92/75/1986-hi-star-aft-cabin-power-10069275-20260309214955793-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774980543000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/92/75/1986-hi-star-aft-cabin-power-10069275-20260129224003851-4.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774980543000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/92/75/1986-hi-star-aft-cabin-power-10069275-20260331110440325-1.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774981198000&exact=&format=webp"]', 'Boat DetailsDescriptionIntroducing the exquisite 1986 Hi-Star Aft Cabin, a stunning vessel that combines elegance with performance. With an overall length of 48 feet, this semi-displacement fiberglass hull is designed for both comfort and efficiency on the water. Powered by twin Caterpillar 3208 TA diesel engines, each delivering an impressive 355 horsepower, it promises a cruising speed of 14 knots and a maximum hull speed of 18 knots, ensuring a thrilling experience for all aboard. The interior boasts two well-appointed cabins and two heads, providing ample space for relaxation and privacy. The electric windlass enhances convenience during anchoring, making your adventures even more enjoyable. Whether you''re exploring coastal waters or embarking on longer journeys, the Panaseaya is equipped to meet your needs with style and reliability. Experience the perfect blend of luxury and performance with this remarkable vessel, ready to create unforgettable memories on the water.Show MoreContact InformationPlease contact Gerry Purcell at (310) 701-5960Other DetailsDisclaimerThe Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors, to investigate such details as the buyer desires validated. This vessel is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal without notice.Need more details?Ask the sellerPropulsionEngine 1Engine Make:CaterpillarEngine Model:3208 TAEngine Year:1986Total Power:355hpEngine Hours:2500Engine Type:InboardDrive Type:Direct DriveFuel Type:DieselPropeller Type:4 BladePropeller Material:BronzeEngine 2Engine Make:CaterpillarEngine Model:3208 TAEngine Year:1986Total Power:355hpEngine Hours:25…', '2026-04-01T17:42:27.981Z', '2026-04-01T17:42:27.981Z', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Please contact Gerry Purcell at (310) 701-5960', 'Gerry Purcell', '(310) 701-5960', 'DisclaimerThe Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors, to investigate such details as the buyer desires validated. This vessel is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal without notice.', 'The Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors,