er', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/88/32/2000-hatteras-70-convertible-power-9948832-20260305164531861-0.jpg?w=400&h=267&t=1772757932000&exact&format=webp"]', 'Boat DetailsDescription Make Offer!!!!..... Price reduced $75k........Two Boat Owner wants this boat sold Extremely clean example of the capable and well designed Hatteras 70 EB. Upgraded 1800 hp MTUs with 4 Stateroom 4 Heads ..Experienced owner has added many options to make her comfortable for extended cruising/fishing. Highlights include but not limited to (2) SEAKEEPER 9 Gyros , WESMAR Digital stabilizers with oversize fins, (3) Generators , Ice Chipper , Starlink SAT Com ,Custom long range fuel tanks ect ect .... Best Value in her class !! Show MoreContact InformationPlease contact Scott Veach at 866-607-5471Other DetailsAccomodationsThis impressive yacht provides the dedicated sportfisherman with the best of all worlds. She was designed for an owner who demands luxury accommodations with the elegance and amenities of a custom built home and this is combined with the renowned Hatteras ruggedness that allows you to tackle all fishing waters.Thanks to a wide-open salon with galley and dinette forward and a roomy four-stateroom arrangement the 70 Convertible offers the comfort usually reserved for a much larger motor yacht. All staterooms have their own private head and the mid-ship full-beam Master is not only spacious but extremely elegant. Outside you will find an observation deck sheltered by a bridge overhang, that over looks the massive 160 square foot cockpit. The flybridge is dominated by a state-of-the-art helm console and there is plenty of guest seating for cruising with a view or casual entertaining aboard.Engine NotesMains have approx 5000 hours , recent services 2025 include New injectors, New injector pumps, Raw water pumps , Heat Exchanger and Intercoolers serviced , Exhaust manifolds removed and new gasket. Both Mains equipped with ZF transmission tra…', '2026-03-31T21:00:25.588Z', '2026-03-31T21:00:25.588Z', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Please contact Scott Veach at 866-607-5471', 'Scott Veach', '866-607-5471', 'AccomodationsThis impressive yacht provides the dedicated sportfisherman with the best of all worlds. She was designed for an owner who demands luxury accommodations with the elegance and amenities of a custom built home and this is combined with the renowned Hatteras ruggedness that allows you to tackle all fishing waters.Thanks to a wide-open salon with galley and dinette forward and a roomy four-stateroom arrangement the 70 Convertible offers the comfort usually reserved for a much larger motor yacht. All staterooms have their own private head and the mid-ship full-beam Master is not only spacious but extremely elegant. Outside you will find an observation deck sheltered by a bridge overhang, that over looks the massive 160 square foot cockpit. The flybridge is dominated by a state-of-the-art helm console and there is plenty of guest seating for cruising with a view or casual entertaining aboard.Engine NotesMains have approx 5000 hours , recent services 2025 include New injectors, New injector pumps, Raw water pumps , Heat Exchanger and Intercoolers serviced , Exhaust manifolds removed and new gasket. Both Mains equipped with ZF transmission trailing pumps ( PTOs) as well as bot…', 'The Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors, to investigate such details as the buyer desires validated. This vessel is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal without notice.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Engine 1Engine Make:MTUEngine Model:16V2000Engine Year:2000Total Power:1800hpEngine Hours:5000Engine Type:InboardDrive Type:Direct DriveFuel Type:DieselEngine 2Engine Make:MTUEngine Model:16V2000Engine Year:2000Total Power:1800hpEngine Hours:5000Engine Type:InboardDrive Type:Direct DriveFuel Type:Diesel', 'MTU', '16V2000', '2000', '1800hp', '5000', 'Inboard', 'Direct Drive', 'Diesel', NULL, NULL, 'DimensionsLength Overall:70ftMax Bridge Clearance:18.17ftMax Draft:6.08ftBeam:18ftCabin Headroom:6.5ftWeightsDry Weight:114,500LbMiscellaneousHull Material:FiberglassHull Shape:Deep VeeTanksFresh Water Tank:365 gal Fuel Tank:2000 gal Holding Tank:80 gal AccommodationsGuest Cabins:3Guest Heads:4Crew Cabins:1', NULL, NULL, NULL, '70ft', '18.17ft', '6.08ft', NULL, '18ftCabin Headroom:6.5ft', '114,500Lb', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Fiberglass', 'Deep Vee', NULL, '365 gal', '2000 gal', '80 gal', '4Crew Cabins:1', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/88/32/2000-hatteras-70-convertible-power-9948832-20260305164531861-0.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1772757932000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/62/70/2000-hatteras-70-convertible-power-9726270-20250324113123674-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1772757932000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/62/70/2000-hatteras-70-convertible-power-9726270-20250324113111789-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1772757932000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/62/70/2000-hatteras-70-convertible-power-9726270-20250324113022101-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1772757932000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/62/70/2000-hatteras-70-convertible-power-9726270-20250324113033851-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1772757932000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/62/70/2000-hatteras-70-convertible-power-9726270-20250324113046311-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1772757932000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/62/70/2000-hatteras-70-convertible-power-9726270-20250324113059673-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1772757932000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/62/70/2000-hatteras-70-convertible-power-9726270-20250324113136584-1_XLARGE.j