re by appointment only. Main photo is a stock image. Additional pictures coming soon. This “Trawler by Beneteau” is fast and highly seaworthy, designed for ocean cruising. She is at home on all seas and her consistent energy efficiency makes her a world leader in her category. The Swift Trawler 44 is the result of a joint collaboration by the Beneteau design office, the architect Michel Joubert and the designer Pierre Frutschi. Underway, her semi-displacement hull offers very enjoyable sensations at all speeds, as well as terrific stability as she breaks through the waves. She is timelessly elegant, combining classic style and great modernity.', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/50/19/2019-beneteau-swift-trawler-44-power-9845019-20250724080446393-1.jpg?w=1920&h=267&t=1753369486000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/50/19/2019-beneteau-swift-trawler-44-power-9845019-20250724080448754-1.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1753369489000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/50/19/2019-beneteau-swift-trawler-44-power-9845019-20250724080451395-1.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1753369492000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/50/19/2019-beneteau-swift-trawler-44-power-9845019-20250724080454541-1.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1753369495000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/50/19/2019-beneteau-swift-trawler-44-power-9845019-20250724080457869-1.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1753369499000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/50/19/2019-beneteau-swift-trawler-44-power-9845019-20250724080500662-1.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1753369501000&exact=&format=webp"]', 'Boat DetailsDescriptionHere''s your chance to own the much sought after Beneteau Swift Trawler 44! Lift kept by one owner since new, this vessel is the definition of immaculate condition. Stand out features include: * Only 200 Engine Hours * Diesel Generator * Upgraded Upholstery Throughout * Electric Grill On The Flybridge * Large Teak Table On Flybridge * Optional Additional Cockpit Seating * Great Loop Edition Boat * All Service Work Has Been Done By The Warranty Dealer Since New She is located offsite at the owner''s residence, tours are by appointment only. Main photo is a stock image. Additional pictures coming soon. This “Trawler by Beneteau” is fast and highly seaworthy, designed for ocean cruising. She is at home on all seas and her consistent energy efficiency makes her a world leader in her category. The Swift Trawler 44 is the result of a joint collaboration by the Beneteau design office, the architect Michel Joubert and the designer Pierre Frutschi. Underway, her semi-displacement hull offers very enjoyable sensations at all speeds, as well as terrific stability as she breaks through the waves. She is timelessly elegant, combining classic style and great modernity. Show MoreOther DetailsDisclaimerThe Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors, to investigate such details as the buyer desires validated. This vessel is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal without notice.Need more details?Ask the sellerFeaturesElectrical EquipmentGenerator:✓Inverter:✓ElectronicsRadar:✓Plotter:✓Autopilot:✓GPS:✓VHF:✓Inside EquipmentWashing Machine:✓Microwave Oven:✓Air Conditioning:✓Electric…', '2026-04-01T18:13:43.666Z', '2026-04-01T18:13:43.666Z', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'DisclaimerThe Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors, to investigate such details as the buyer desires validated. This vessel is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal without notice.', 'The Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors, to investigate such details as the buyer desires validated. This vessel is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal without notice.', 'Electrical EquipmentGenerator:✓Inverter:✓ElectronicsRadar:✓Plotter:✓Autopilot:✓GPS:✓VHF:✓Inside EquipmentWashing Machine:✓Microwave Oven:✓Air Conditioning:✓Electric Head:✓Heating:✓Hot Water:✓Refrigerator:✓Deep Freezer:✓', 'Generator | Inverter', 'Radar | Plotter | Autopilot | GPS | VHF', 'Washing Machine | Microwave Oven | Air Conditioning | Electric Head | Heating | Hot Water | Refrigerator | Deep Freezer', NULL, NULL, 'Engine 1Engine Make:VolvoEngine Model:D4Total Power:300hpEngine Hours:200Engine Type:Inboard/OutboardFuel Type:DieselEngine 2Engine Make:VolvoEngine Model:D4Total Power:300hpEngine Hours:200Engine Type:Inboard/OutboardFuel Type:Diesel', 'Volvo', 'D4', NULL, '300hp', '200', 'Inboard/Outboard', NULL, 'Diesel', NULL, NULL, 'DimensionsLength Overall:45.5ftBeam:13.92ftWeightsDry Weight:23,957LbMiscellaneousHull Material:FiberglassTanksFresh Water Tank:169 gal Fuel Tank:370 gal Holding Tank:32 gal AccommodationsGuest Cabins:2Guest Heads:2', NULL, NULL, NULL, '45.5ft', NULL, NULL, NULL, '13.92ft', '23,957Lb', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Fiberglass', NULL, NULL, '169 gal', '370 gal', '32 gal', '2', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/50/19/2019-beneteau-swift-trawler-44-power-9845019-20250724080446393-1.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1753369486000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/50/19/2019-beneteau-swift-trawler-44-power-9845019-20250724080448754-1.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1753369489000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/50/19/2019-beneteau-swift-trawler-44-power-9845019-20250724080451395-1.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1753369492000&exact&format=webp","https