cruiser can look, feel and preform. Key Features Out Here Time Expands - Enjoy every moment in a signature Sea Ray Sundancer. Every inch of a Sea Ray cruiser is attended to with expertly appointed textures, finishes and details that transform a beautiful boat into a second home. Solid-surfaced countertops, stainless-steel trim, fully finishes head compartments and multi-tone upholstery shine below with a gleam that invites you to stay. Take a Bow - Expansive open bow lounging and seating area with actuated headrest and armrests on the Sundancer 320 Outboard, allow for perfect comfort while underway or at rest. Own Your Command Center- The intuitive helm station on the Sundancer 320 Outboard features a Dual Digital Dash with Simrad touchscreen displays. The dual helm seat provides all day comfort for navigating your favorite waters. Thrilling Outboard Power - Outboard power comes with zero tradeoff in terms of space, comfort, or enjoyment on the Sea Ray Sundancer 320 Outboard. This boat is powered by standard twin Mercury 350 Verado V10 outboard engines with joystick piloting, SmartCraft Digital Throttle and Shift (DTS) and e-steering. Advanced Helm Station - The intuitive helm station features Dual Digital Dash with Simrad touchscreen displays, ensuring…', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/47/23/2026-sea-ray-sundancer-320-outboard-power-10004723-20251106080328631-0.jpg?w=1920&h=267&t=1774879606000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/47/23/2026-sea-ray-sundancer-320-outboard-power-10004723-20251106080328643-1.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774879605000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/47/23/2026-sea-ray-sundancer-320-outboard-power-10004723-20251106080328654-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774879606000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/47/23/2026-sea-ray-sundancer-320-outboard-power-10004723-20251106080328664-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774879605000&exact=&format=webp"