ng, SmartCraft Digital Throttle and Shift (DTS) and e-steering. Advanced Helm Station - The intuitive helm station features Dual Digital Dash with Simrad touchsc…', '2026-04-01T18:12:07.966Z', '2026-04-01T18:12:07.966Z', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Engine 1Engine Make:MERCURYEngine Model:WHT 400 JPO V10Total Power:400hpEngine Type:OutboardDrive Type:OtherFuel Type:GasEngine 2Engine Make:MERCURYEngine Model:WHT 400 JPO V10Total Power:400hpEngine Type:OutboardFuel Type:Gas', 'MERCURY', 'WHT 400 JPO V10', NULL, '400hp', NULL, 'Outboard', 'Other', 'Gas', NULL, NULL, 'DimensionsLength Overall:32ftMax Draft:3.67ftMin Draft:2.67ftBeam:10.58ftWeightsDry Weight:14,566LbMiscellaneousWindlass:Hydraulic WindlassDeadrise At Transom:21degElectrical Circuit:noneHull Material:FiberglassHull Shape:OtherKeel Type:OtherTanksFresh Water Tank:32 gal Fuel Tank:220 gal Holding Tank:27 gal AccommodationsGuest Heads:1', NULL, NULL, NULL, '32ft', NULL, '3.67ft', '2.67ft', '10.58ft', '14,566Lb', 'Hydraulic Windlass', 'none', '21deg', 'Fiberglass', 'Other', 'Other', '32 gal', '220 gal', '27 gal', '1', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/47/23/2026-sea-ray-sundancer-320-outboard-power-10004723-20251106080328631-0.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1774879606000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/47/23/2026-sea-ray-sundancer-320-outboard-power-10004723-20251106080328643-1.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1774879605000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/47/23/2026-sea-ray-sundancer-320-outboard-power-10004723-20251106080328654-2.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1774879606000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/47/23/2026-sea-ray-sundancer-320-outboard-power-10004723-20251106080328664-3.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1774879605000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/47/23/2026-sea-ray-sundancer-320-outboard-power-10004723-20251106080328674-4.jpg?w=1028&ratio=de