, and an adjustable bow table that can be retracted completely to the floor or converted to a full lounge (bow filler cushion included). Fishing features include twin insulated fish boxes, dual aerated livewells, multiple rod holders, and an expansive cockpit. A fiberglass T-top with rod storage and a super deluxe drop bolster leaning post add to its offshore capability and comfort. Powered by twin Yamaha outboards and backed by Tidewater’s limited lifetime hull warranty, the 282 CC is a natural choice for your offshore adventures. Specifications: Hull Color: Oyster Accent Color: Oyster hardtop underside & console faceplate color, White waterline stripe Cushion Color: White/Black Power: Twin Yamaha F 250 XSB2 (White) About Blue Water Boats Blue Water Boats is your trusted Tidewater dealer in Cape May Courthouse, NJ. In addition to new and used boat sales, we offer in-house financing, trailers, and expert service to keep you on the water. Contact us today to see the 2026 Tidewater 282 CC in person!', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/82/37/2026-tidewater-282-cc-adventure-power-9958237-20250924144459030-1.jpg?w=1920&h=267&t=1758751202000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/82/37/2026-tidewater-282-cc-adventure-power-9958237-20250924144500005-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1758751203000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/82/37/2026-tidewater-282-cc-adventure-power-9958237-20260205135654982-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1770329517000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/82/37/2026-tidewater-282-cc-adventure-power-9958237-20260205135642661-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1770329505000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/82/37/2026-tidewater-282-cc-adventure-power-9958237-20260205135643842-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1770329506000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/82/37/2026-tidewater-282-cc-adventure-power-9958237-2026020513564481