is delivered exactly as expected.• On-Water Training – Hands-on coaching with a certified delivery captain covering docking, maneuvering, navigation, and any skills you’d like to practice.• Service Department Turnover – A coordinated hand-off with our service team to set you up for long-term success and confidence.• Ongoing Support – Our goal is to make sure you feel ready, supported, and excited to enjoy your new boat from day one. Full Description The 2026 Ranger Tugs R‑25 is a nimble cruiser built for comfort and versatility. With a GRP planing hull, it measures 28''5" LOA and 8''6" beam, easily towable yet spacious onboard. A 250 hp Yamaha F250 outboard, paired with electric steering (DES), trim tabs, Laminar Flow Interrupters, and an optional bow thruster, delivers smooth, confident handling. The walk-in helm surrounds you with light and views thanks to a curved windshield, four skylights, sliding side windows, and an opening glass bulkhead. Below deck, the vessel boasts a private forward stateroom, mid-berth, and a dinette that converts to a bed, comfortably sleeping four. The galley includes a refrigerator/freezer, stovetop, microwave, sink, and ample storage. A fully enclosed head with shower ensures convenience, while…', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/24/82/2026-ranger-tugs-r-25-power-9942482-20260331103246993-1.jpg?w=1920&h=267&t=1774979269000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/24/82/2026-ranger-tugs-r-25-power-9942482-20260331103247696-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774979273000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/24/82/2026-ranger-tugs-r-25-power-9942482-20260331103248490-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774979271000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/24/82/2026-ranger-tugs-r-25-power-9942482-20260331103249090-4.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774979274000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/24/82/2026-ranger-tugs-r-25-power-9942482-2026