 Battery Switch Seaspray Hull Sides & White Bottom Road King Tandem Axle Trailer - Included *Tidewater LifePLUS warranty includes: ~2 Year Bow-to-Stern coverage LIFETIME Limited Structural Hull coverage *Transfer fee may apply This Carolina Bay model provides customers with an efficient stepped bottom hull, large bow casting deck, dual livewells, and recessed bow seating. The 2500 Carolina Bay is the complete package for family and fishing. The ride and performance of this hull is unmatched by any 25ft. bay boat in the industry.', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/21/90/2025-tidewater-2500-carolina-bay-power-10132190-20260330055105487-1.jpg?w=1920&h=267&t=1774875969000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/21/90/2025-tidewater-2500-carolina-bay-power-10132190-20260330055106289-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774875970000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/21/90/2025-tidewater-2500-carolina-bay-power-10132190-20260330055107038-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774875971000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/21/90/2025-tidewater-2500-carolina-bay-power-10132190-20260330055107769-4.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774875972000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/21/90/2025-tidewater-2500-carolina-bay-power-10132190-20260330055116086-1.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774875980000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/21/90/2025-tidewater-2500-carolina-bay-power-10132190-20260330055116838-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774875980000&exact=&format=webp"]', 'Boat DetailsDescription2025 Tidewater 2500 Carolina Bay Equipped Options & Features include: Mercury V10 Verado 400 (46 hrs) Mercury Vessel View Garmin 1243xsv Garmin B75 TH Transducer Power Pole Blade 8'' JL Audio MM105 w/ 6x JL Audio Speakers, Amp, & 10" Subwoofer Powder Coated Fiberglass T-Top w/ Full Glass Enclosure & Vent LectroTab Trim Tabs w/ Indicators White Powder Coat Deluxe Drop Bols