grand fishing scene a lot over the years as she was mainly kept local by her original private owner until just a season or so ago. This says a lot about a boat...Take advantage of this recent opportunity to get into a 56 foot battleship that is a beast and has loads of potential. Give us a call!', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/70/17/2000-custom-carolina-55-east-bay-power-9597017-20241029101438538-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=400&h=267&t=1767627346000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/70/17/2000-custom-carolina-55-east-bay-power-9597017-20241105180549486-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1767627346000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/70/17/2000-custom-carolina-55-east-bay-power-9597017-20241029101442365-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1767627346000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/70/17/2000-custom-carolina-55-east-bay-power-9597017-20241105180552538-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1767627346000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/70/17/2000-custom-carolina-55-east-bay-power-9597017-20241105180547523-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1767627346000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/70/17/2000-custom-carolina-55-east-bay-power-9597017-20241029101443377-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1767627346000&exact&format=webp"]', 'Boat DetailsDescriptionOWNERS MOTIVATED TO SELL / GREAT SEA BOAT / STABLE FISHING PLATFORM If you''re looking for a big, beamy, beautiful Custom Carolina hull, take a look at WOODCUTTER. She was built in 2000 by Ricky Gillikin and East Bay Boatworks and powered with a pair of 900hp MTUs with only 3700 original hours currently. She offers an incomparable ride and moving around her cockpit, bridge and interior, she operates like a much bigger boat. She cruises at 27kt and has 6 total berths and 2 full heads. This boat hasn''t been center stage on the grand fishing scene a lot over the years as she was main