 Salon, as well as a U-shaped dinette and fiberglass Hi-Lo table. The Cockpit of the 37 Billfish is the largest in its class offering 86 square feet of area and Mezzanine seating. Below Deck is an L-shaped Galley, Head with an enclosed shower and a large Forward Stateroom with a single centerline queen berth and two hanging lockers. Twin Cummins QSB 6.7 550HP Diesel w/ 1335 Hours ONAN 9kW Generator w/ 1559 Hours SeaKeeper SK-5 Gyro Stabilizer Cummins Joystick System w/Bow Thruster Garmin Electronics New in 2024 / 2025 Kingston Gray Hull Color Command Deck Lower Helm Command Deck A/C Cockpit Covers Winter Flybridge Covers All Systems Serviced w/ Records Available', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/98/48/2018-viking-37-billfish-power-9959848-20251001183127785-1.jpg?w=400&h=267&t=1759370064000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/98/48/2018-viking-37-billfish-power-9959848-20251003070631807-1.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1759501296000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/98/48/2018-viking-37-billfish-power-9959848-20251001184654357-3.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1759500496000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/98/48/2018-viking-37-billfish-power-9959848-20251001184646720-4.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1759370510000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/98/48/2018-viking-37-billfish-power-9959848-20251001184649194-1.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1759370511000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/98/48/2018-viking-37-billfish-power-9959848-20251001184644574-1.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1759370507000&exact&format=webp"]', 'Boat DetailsDescriptionNEW TO MARKET! NEW GARMIN ELECTRONICS!! LOADED WITH OPTIONS AND UPGRADES!!! METICULOUSLY SERVICED AND MAINTAINED!!! SHE IS TURN KEY!!! Designed with the owners in mind, the 37 Billfish offers the versatility of a cruising boat and the simplicity and ease of maintenance needed for a ready-to-go fishing machine. The tournament-style Center Console Walk-Around Helm of the 37 Billfish features one Helm chair, standard for this model, with the option to add a second Helm chair to the Flybridge. On the Command Deck, you will find a living area with the feel of a Salon, as well as a U-shaped dinette and fiberglass Hi-Lo table. The Cockpit of the 37 Billfish is the largest in its class offering 86 square feet of area and Mezzanine seating. Below Deck is an L-shaped Galley, Head with an enclosed shower and a large Forward Stateroom with a single centerline queen berth and two hanging lockers. Twin Cummins QSB 6.7 550HP Diesel w/ 1335 Hours ONAN 9kW Generator w/ 1559 Hours SeaKeeper SK-5 Gyro Stabilizer Cummins Joystick System w/Bow Thruster Garmin Electronics New in 2024 / 2025 Kingston Gray Hull Color Command Deck Lower Helm Command Deck A/C Cockpit Covers Winter Flybridge Covers All Systems Serviced w/ Records Available Show MoreContact InformationPlease contact Roger Mooney at 410-456-3659Other DetailsGalley Aluminum Cabin Door, Access To Command Deck High Glossed Juno Teak Interior Wood Throughout Polished Sahara Corian Countertop, Stainless Sink w/ Satin Nickel Faucet Kenyon Electric (2) Burner Recessed Cooktop w/ Cover Exhaust Fan Teak & Maple Amtico Flooring Headliner, Opus, Natural Color, 1/8" Foam & Tricot Backing Overhead LED Lighting Main Electrical Service Panel, AC/DC, Backlit For Easy Viewing Samsung Microwave/Convection Oven Located In Upper…', '2026-03-31T20:58:49.238Z', '2026-03-31T20:58:49.238Z', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Please contact Roger Mooney at 410-456-3659', 'Roger Mooney', '410-456-3659', 'Galley Aluminum Cabin Door, Access To Command Deck High Glossed Juno Teak Interior Wood Throughout Polished Sahara Corian Countertop, Stainless Sink w/ Satin Nickel Faucet Kenyon Electric (2) Burner Recessed Cooktop w/ Cover Exhaust Fan Teak & Maple Amtico Flooring Headliner, Opus, Natural Color, 1/8" Foam & Tricot Backing Overhead LED Lighting Main Electrical Service Panel, AC/DC, Backlit For Easy Viewing Samsung Microwave/Convection Oven Located In Upper Galley Cabinet Isotherm Refrigerator/Freezer, Under-Counter Drawer Style New in 2022 Storage Cabinets In Upper Galley w/ Varnished Doors, Finished Maple Interior Storage Cabinets & Drawers In Lower Galley, Finished Maple Interior MASTER STATEROOM Air Conditioning w/ Reverse Cycle Heat & Temperature Control (Services Entire Interior) Island Berth w/ Innerspring Mattress Custom Bed Spread, Quilted Designer Style w/ Pillows & Shams, Fitted Sheet Set Amtico Flooring Teak & Maple Bomar Hatch Foredeck Hatch w/ Screen & Shade System Opus Natural Color Headliner Foam & Tricot Backing Throughout 24 Volt Overhead Recessed Lighting in Headliner Portside Rod Locker (Fits 7’ Rods) Fusion Stereo System w/ Speakers Samsung 20" Flat Screen TV SH…', 'Engine and generator hours are as of the date of the original listing and are a representation of what the listing broker is told by the owner and/or actual reading of the engine hour meters. The broker cannot guarantee the true hours. It is the responsibility of the purchaser and/or his agent to verify engine hours, warranties implied or otherwise and major overhauls as well as all other representations noted on the listing.DisclaimerWhile we attempt to display current and accurate data, this listing may not reflect the most recent transactions or may contain occasional data entry errors. Selling agent makes no warranties, express or implied, regarding the content or availability of the products described herein. All inventory listed is subject to availability and prior sale. Please consu…', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Engine 1Engine Make:CumminsEngine Model:Cummins QSB6.7Engine Year:2017Total Power:550hpEngine Hours:1335Engine Type:InboardDrive Type:Direct DriveFuel Type:DieselPropeller Type:4 BladePropeller Material:BronzeEngine 2Engine Make:CumminsEngine Model:Cummins QSB6.7Engine Year:2017Total Power:550hpEngine Hours:1335Engine Type:InboardDrive Type:Direct DriveFuel Type:DieselPropeller Type:4 BladePropeller Material:Bronze', 'Cummins', 'Cummins QSB6.7', '2017', '550hp', '1335', 'Inboard', 'Direct Drive', 'Diesel', '4 Blade', 'Bronze', 'Speed & DistanceCruising Speed:30knMax Speed:34knDimensionsLength Overall:37ftMax Draft:2.67ftBeam:13.83ftMiscellaneousSeating Capacity:10Deadrise At Transom:12.5degElectrical Circuit:220VHull Material:FiberglassHull Shape:Modified VeeTanksFresh Water Tank:1 x 66 gal Fuel Tank:1 x 440 gal Holding Tank:1 x 35 gal AccommodationsGuest Cabins:1Guest Heads:1', '30kn', '34kn', NULL, '37ft', NULL, '2.67ft', NULL, '13.83ft', NULL, NULL, '220V', '12.5deg', 'Fiberglass', 'Modified Vee', NULL, '1 x 66 gal', '1 x 440 gal', '1 x 35 gal', '1', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/98/48/2018-viking-37-billfish-power-9959848-20251001183127785-1.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1759370064000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/98/48/2018-viking-37-billfish-power-9959848-20251003070631807-1.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1759501296000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/98/48/2018-viking-37-billfish-power-9959848-20251001184654357-3.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1759500496000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/98/48/2018-viking-37-billfish-power-9959848-20251001184646720-4.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1759370510000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/98/48/2018-viking-37-billfish-power-9959848-20251001184649194-1.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1759370511000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/98/48/2018-viking-37-billfish-power-9959848-20251001184644574-1.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1759370507000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/98/48/2018-viking-37-billfish-power-9959848-20251001184649734-2.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1759370512000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/98/48/2018-viking-37-billfish-power-9959848-20251001184650071-3.jpg?w