raftsmanship and Luxury The Boston Whaler 325 Conquest showcases exquisite craftsmanship with high-end finishes and thoughtful design elements, ensuring every detail is catered to your comfort. Luxurious amenities provide a welcoming atmosphere, making this vessel a beautiful retreat on the water. Buy with Confidence When you choose MarineMax Huntington in Huntington, NY, you receive unparalleled benefits, including a full fuel tank and a Go Boating Gear kit to keep you safe. Enjoy no-hassle financing, exceptional service with online scheduling, and expert guidance through our boating classes. Get ready for endless fun with boat shows, customer events, and exclusive Getaways!® trips. This is your opportunity to own a superbly designed vessel—make the 2026 Boston Whaler 325 Conquest your next adventure!', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/67/76/2026-boston-whaler-325-conquest-power-9966776-20260324113949056-1.jpg?w=1920&h=267&t=1774879472000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/67/76/2026-boston-whaler-325-conquest-power-9966776-20260324113949109-0.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774879476000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/67/76/2026-boston-whaler-325-conquest-power-9966776-20260324113949098-4.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774879476000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/67/76/2026-boston-whaler-325-conquest-power-9966776-20260324113957379-5.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774879475000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/67/76/2026-boston-whaler-325-conquest-power-9966776-20260324113957501-6.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774879473000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/67/76/2026-boston-whaler-325-conquest-power-9966776-20260324113957482-8.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774879473000&exact=&format=webp"]', 'Boat DetailsDescription Just landed and ready to make waves! Embark on your next adventure with the stunning 2026 Boston Whaler 325 Conquest, a perfect blend of luxury and performance. Designed for the discerning boater, this robust vessel is ready to take you wherever the sea beckons. Unmatched Performance Powered by two Mercury WHT 400 JPO VDO V10 AMS engines, boasting a total of 800 hp, the 325 Conquest offers exhilarating speed and agility on the water. Experience the thrill of effortless cruising, whether for a leisurely day on the bay or a weekend getaway. Craftsmanship and Luxury The Boston Whaler 325 Conquest showcases exquisite craftsmanship with high-end finishes and thoughtful design elements, ensuring every detail is catered to your comfort. Luxurious amenities provide a welcoming atmosphere, making this vessel a beautiful retreat on the water. Buy with Confidence When you choose MarineMax Huntington in Huntington, NY, you receive unparalleled benefits, including a full fuel tank and a Go Boating Gear kit to keep you safe. Enjoy no-hassle financing, exceptional service with online scheduling, and expert guidance through our boating classes. Get ready for endless fun with boat shows, customer events, and exclusive Getaways!® trips. This is your opportunity to own a superbly designed vessel—make the 2026 Boston Whaler 325 Conquest your next adventure!Show MorePropulsionEngine 1Engine Make:MERCURYEngine Model:WHT 400 JPO VDO V10 AMSTotal Power:400hpEngine Type:OutboardDrive Type:OtherFuel Type:GasEngine 2Engine Make:MERCURYEngine Model:WHT 400 JPO VDO V10 AMSTotal Power:400hpEngine Type:OutboardFuel Type:GasSpecificationsDimensionsLength Overall:32ftMin Draft:2.17ftBeam:10.67ftWeightsDry Weight:10,500LbMiscellaneousWindlass:Hydraulic WindlassDeadrise At Transom…', '2026-04-01T18:12:12.479Z', '2026-04-01T18:12:12.479Z', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Engine 1Engine Make:MERCURYEngine Model:WHT 400 JPO VDO V10 AMSTotal Power:400hpEngine Type:OutboardDrive Type:OtherFuel Type:GasEngine 2Engine Make:MERCURYEngine Model:WHT 400 JP