xt owner. The spacious cockpit features U-shaped seating, cockpit carpet, and a wet bar with refrigerator, making it perfect for entertaining family and friends. Raymarine electronics provide reliable navigation, while the windlass makes anchoring effortless. Below deck, the cabin is equally impressive with a V-berth, convertible dinette, and fully equipped galley, offering comfortable overnight accommodations. An enclosed head completes the package, making extended trips easy and enjoyable. This Formula 310 SS is a fantastic opportunity to own a premium performance cruiser that’s ready to hit the water.', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/78/17/2015-formula-310-sun-sport-power-10067817-20260128102922793-1.jpg?w=1920&h=267&t=1769625865000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/78/17/2015-formula-310-sun-sport-power-10067817-20260128095927119-4.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1769624973000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/78/17/2015-formula-310-sun-sport-power-10067817-20260128095926327-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1769624973000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/78/17/2015-formula-310-sun-sport-power-10067817-20260128095925966-1.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1769624973000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/78/17/2015-formula-310-sun-sport-power-10067817-20260128095926724-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1769624973000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/78/17/2015-formula-310-sun-sport-power-10067817-20260128100126612-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1769624973000&exact=&format=webp"]', 'Boat DetailsDescription2015 Formula 310 SS – Luxury, Performance & Versatility Experience the ultimate blend of performance, comfort, and Formula’s legendary build quality with this 2015 Formula 310 SS. Designed for everything from adrenaline-filled watersports to relaxed weekend cruising, this vessel delivers an exceptional on-the-water experience. Powe