0&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/41/99/2021-tiara-sport-43-ls-power-9964199-20250930165414071-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1759277358000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/41/99/2021-tiara-sport-43-ls-power-9964199-20250930165413231-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774701773000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/41/99/2021-tiara-sport-43-ls-power-9964199-20250930165412909-1.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774701773000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/41/99/2021-tiara-sport-43-ls-power-9964199-20250930165414879-1.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774701773000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/41/99/2021-tiara-sport-43-ls-power-9964199-20250930165413095-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1774701773000&exact=&format=webp"]', 'Boat DetailsDescriptionYamaha Extended Warranty Through 5/3/2026 MOTIVATED Original Owner YAMAHA ENGINES SERVICED BY DEALER 12/2025 "Carry On" is a loaded, original owner 43 Tiara LS featuring Triple 425 Yamahas, Helm Master, Bow Thruster, Sea Keeper, Cockpit Power Sun Shade, Garmin Chart, Open Array Radar, Bottom Machine, Autopilot, FLIR Night Vision, Generator, Cabin as well as Helm Deck Heat and AC, and Summer Kitchen.Show MoreContact InformationPlease contact J. Eric Smith, CPYB at 781-749-9989Other DetailsAdditional InformationThe 43 LS combines the aesthetic of sport styling with the luxurious amenities and details synonymous with the Tiara Sport brand. Guests can choose from multiple social zones for relaxation and leisure. Forward, the bow features wrap around seating with a reclining lounge. The helm seats four comfortably, with standing room and a leaning bolster just aft, providing a secure zone for more guests while underway. A side boarding door located portside presents access to your favorite water activities. The innovative aft U-lounge rotates 180 allowing guests to further enjoy the swim platform and beautiful views. Entertain everyone aboard from the galley, well equipped with sink, refrigerator and large countertop. Below deck, comfortable accommodations for four await. The sleek styling of the 43 LS is best complemented by power and performance. Yamaha® power combined with glass cockpit integrated electronics including Garmin® Marine navigation systems provide comfort and control at the helm. Optional Yamaha® helm master joystick steering offers an additional level of command at the dock or underway. A fuel capacity of 400 gallons combined with a top speed over 50 mph gets you to your favorite port of call fast, giving you more time to enjoy with fa…', '2026-04-01T18:11:35.914Z', '2026-04-01T18:11:35.914Z', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Please contact J. Eric Smith, CPYB at 781-749-9989', 'J. Eric Smith, CPYB', '781-749-9989', 'Additional InformationThe 43 LS combines the aesthetic of sport styling with the luxurious amenities and details synonymous with the Tiara Sport brand. Guests can choose from multiple social zones for relaxation and leisure. Forward, the bow features wrap around seating with a reclining lounge. The helm seats four comfortably, with standing room and a leaning bolster just aft, providing a secure zone for more guests while underway. A side boarding door located portside presents access to your favorite water activities. The innovative aft U-lounge rotates 180 allowing guests to further enjoy the swim platform and beautiful views. Entertain everyone aboard from the galley, well equipped with sink, refrigerator and large countertop. Below deck, comfortable accommodations for four await. The sleek styling of the 43 LS is best complemented by power and performance. Yamaha® power combined with glass cockpit integrated electronics including Garmin® Marine navigation systems provide comfort and control at the helm. Optional Yamaha® helm master joystick steering offers an additional level of command at the dock or underway. A fuel capacity of 400 gallons combined with a top speed over 50 mp…', 'The Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors, to investigate such details as the buyer desires validated. This vessel is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal without notice.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Engine 1Engine Make:YamahaEngine Model:Four StrokeTotal Power:425hpEngine Hours:495Engine Type:OutboardFuel Type:GasEngine 2Engine Make:YamahaEngine Model:Four StrokeTotal Power:425hpEngine Hours:495Engine Type:OutboardFuel Type:GasEngine 3Engine Make:YamahaEngine Model:Four StrokeTotal Power:425hpEngine Hours:495Engine Type:OutboardFuel Type:Gas', 'Yamaha', 'Four Stroke', NULL, '425hp', '495', 'Outboard', NULL, 'Gas', NULL, NULL, 'DimensionsLength Overall:43ftMax Bridge Clearance:9.33ftMax Draft:3.58ftMin Draft:2.33ftBeam:13ftWeightsDry Weight:21,800LbMiscellaneousDeadrise At Transom:21degHull Material:FiberglassHull Shape:Modified VeeTanksFresh Water Tank:60 gal Fuel Tank:400 gal Holding Tank:40 gal', NULL, NULL, NULL, '43ft', '9.33ft', '3.58ft', '2.33ft', '13ft', '21,800Lb', NULL, NULL, '21deg', 'Fiberglass', 'Modified Vee', NULL, '60 gal', '400 gal', '40 gal', NULL, '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/41/99/2021-tiara-sport-43-ls-power-9964199-20250930165414995-2.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1774701773000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/41/99/2021-tiara-sport-43-ls-power-9964199-20250930165414071-3.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1759277358000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/41/99/2021-tiara-sport-43-ls-power-9964199-20250930165413231-3.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1774701773000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/41/99/2021-tiara-sport-43-ls-power-9964199-20250930165412909-1.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1774701773000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgrou