ime you set out. Overview The 2026 Sportsman Heritage 231 is a 23-foot Center Console boat that embodies the spirit of adventure and relaxation. Measuring 23.33 feet in length, this new model offers ample space for friends and family, while its sleek lines and modern design ensure you’ll turn heads at every marina. The Heritage 231 is engineered for both coastal cruising and offshore excursions, making it a versatile choice for a wide range of boating activities. Whether you’re planning a leisurely day at the sandbar or an action-packed fishing trip, this Sportsman boat for sale is built to exceed expectations. Performance At the heart of the Heritage 231 is the powerful Yamaha F300XSB engine, finished in a striking white. With an impressive 300 horsepower, this Center Console boat delivers exhilarating acceleration, smooth cruising, and reliable performance in a variety of conditions. The Yamaha F300XSB is renowned for its efficiency, quiet operation, and responsive handling, ensuring that every outing is as enjoyable as it is memorable. Whether you’re navigating choppy waters or gliding across calm bays, the Heritage 231’s performance capabilities inspire confidence and excitement. Features and Specifications The Sportsman Heritage 231 is loaded with features…', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/75/89/2026-sportsman-heritage-231-center-console-power-9807589-20260212011035914-1.jpg?w=1920&h=267&t=1773164873000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/75/89/2026-sportsman-heritage-231-center-console-power-9807589-20260212011035926-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1773164876000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/75/89/2026-sportsman-heritage-231-center-console-power-9807589-20260213010934475-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1773164874000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/75/89/2026-sportsman-heritage-231-center-console-power-9807589-20260212011035935-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1