acht, measuring 43.5 feet in length and crafted to deliver an unforgettable boating experience. As a new model, it showcases the latest advancements in yacht design and technology, ensuring you enjoy every moment on the water. The sleek hull, finished in the eye-catching Axalta Lunar Blue with a striking Axalta Crystal White bootstripe, gives this yacht a commanding presence at any marina or anchorage. The 43 LS is a testament to Tiara Yachts’ commitment to quality, style, and performance, making it a top choice for discerning boaters seeking a yacht boat for sale that truly stands out. Performance Power and precision are at the heart of the Tiara Yachts 43 LS. Equipped with twin Mercury 600 V12 Verado outboard engines, this yacht delivers a combined 1,200 horsepower, ensuring exhilarating speed and smooth handling. The advanced engineering of these engines provides not only impressive acceleration but also remarkable fuel efficiency, allowing you to explore further with confidence. Whether you are cruising along the coastline or embarking on longer journeys, the 43 LS offers a responsive and agile ride, making every outing a thrilling adventure. The Seakeeper SK6 Gyro stabilizer further enhances your experience by minimizin…', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/75/31/2026-tiara-yachts-43-ls-power-9807531-20260218011008790-1.jpg?w=1920&h=267&t=1772574411000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/75/31/2026-tiara-yachts-43-ls-power-9807531-20260218011008544-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1772574419000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/75/31/2026-tiara-yachts-43-ls-power-9807531-20260218011008771-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1772574412000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/75/31/2026-tiara-yachts-43-ls-power-9807531-20260218011008574-4.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1772574435000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/75/31/2026-tiara-yachts-43-ls-power-9807