 Fiber telescoping poles and huge livewell and fishbox capacity. Aft mezzanine seat with prep & tackle center and overhead SureShade® provide additional cockpit seating without compromising fishing amenities. Easy tower access makes the dual helm even more attractive and below deck, the newly-redesigned cabin features Chilewich interiors, galley kitchen, double berth, and spacious head with shower, allowing you to accommodate friends and family with ease.', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/92/18/2022-regulator-41-power-10049218-20260106122256640-1.jpg?w=400&h=267&t=1767731885000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/92/18/2022-regulator-41-power-10049218-20260106122256193-4.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1767731923000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/92/18/2022-regulator-41-power-10049218-20260106122255976-2.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1767731889000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/92/18/2022-regulator-41-power-10049218-20260106122255830-1.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1767731938000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/92/18/2022-regulator-41-power-10049218-20260106122257607-1.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1767731882000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/92/18/2022-regulator-41-power-10049218-20260106122257091-4.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1767731945000&exact&format=webp"]', 'Boat DetailsDescriptionPowered by quad Yamaha 425s with Helm Master® EX and equipped with Seakeeper® 5, the 41 meets your every offshore need. The new Offshore Command Center features Garmin® Multi-Function Display with Digital Switching and Monitoring, along with proprietary Regulator MyHelm™ interface to seamlessly and intuitively connect key functions in one application – with wireless key fob to trigger lighting, batteries, and more as you approach or disembark with the touch of a button. Serious anglers will love the Taco® Grand Slam 500 outrigger bases with 20’ 