2021 Ranger 2510 Bay – The Ultimate Hybrid Predator 
If you’re looking for the "Swiss Army Knife" of the saltwater world, you just found it. This 2021 Ranger 2510 Bay is a masterclass in versatility, designed for the angler who wants to stalk the flats at dawn and punch through a coastal chop for offshore wrecks by noon. 
Ranger’s "Big Bay" philosophy is on full display here: a massive, stable fishing platform paired with the refined comfort and safety that only a foam-filled, pultruded fiberglass hull can provide. 
Top-Tier Specifications 
 
 Length: 24'' 10" 
 Beam: 102" (An incredibly wide, stable stance) 
 Fuel Capacity: 97 Gallons 
 Draft: Approx. 14" (Engine up) 
 Engine: Mercury 300XL Verado (Digital Throttle & Shift) 
 
Key Features & Angling DNA 
This boat was rigged with a "no-compromise" mindset. Whether you''re live-baiting for tarpon or casting artificials for reds, the layout is intuitive and deadly efficient. 
 
 Massive Casting Decks: Oversized front and rear decks provide 360-degree fishability with premium non-skid surfaces. 
 Advanced Livewell System: Features a high-capacity aerated livewell with timers and high-speed pickups to keep your bait tournament-ready. 
 Integrated Storage: Dedicated port and starboard rod lockers that actually fit full-sized saltwater outfits, plus dry storage tubs that stay dry. 
 The "Ranger Ride": Even in a 2-foot chop, the 2510 remains remarkably dry and stable, thanks to its flared bow and heavy-duty stringer system. 
 
Electronics & Upgrades 
This isn''t just a base model; it’s a fully-outfitted fishing machine: 
 
 Dual 10'' Power-Poles: Essential for silent shallow-water anchoring. 
 Trolling Motor: Minn Kota Riptide Terrova (36V) with i-Pilot Link. 
 Helm Tech: Flush-mounte…', 'The Boat Yard, Inc', 'Bay Boat', '["https://images.boats.com/resize/1/53/48/2021-ranger-2510-bay-power-10075348-20260205144350045-1.jpg?t=1770331431000&w=360&ratio=4:3","https://images.boats.com/resize/1/53/48/2021-ranger-2510-bay-power-10075348-20260205144010936-3.jpg?t=1770331152000&w=900&h=900","https://images.boats.com/resize/1/53/48/2021-ranger-2510-bay-power-10075348-20260205144350045-1.jpg?t=1770331152000&w=900&h=900","https://images.boats.com/resize/1/53/48/2021-ranger-2510-bay-power-10075348-20260205144006441-2.jpg?t=1770331152000&w=900&h=900","https://images.boats.com/resize/1/53/48/2021-ranger-2510-bay-power-10075348-20260205144006612-3.jpg?t=1770331152000&w=900&h=900","https://images.boats.com/resize/1/53/48/2021-ranger-2510-bay-power-10075348-20260205144006735-4.jpg?t=1770331152000&w=900&h=900"]', 'Ranger 2510 Bay

