gth, offering ample space for family, friends, and gear. As a new model, it boasts the latest advancements in marine engineering and design, ensuring you enjoy a cutting-edge boating experience. With its Neptune Gray hull color, this Pursuit boat for sale commands attention at the dock and on the water, blending sleek aesthetics with rugged durability. Whether you’re planning offshore fishing excursions, coastal cruising, or lively gatherings, the S 428 delivers unmatched versatility and style. Performance Powering the Pursuit S 428 are four Yamaha Quad XF450XTO2 engines, delivering a jaw-dropping combined 1800 horsepower. This powerhouse configuration ensures exhilarating speed, smooth acceleration, and reliable performance in a variety of sea conditions. Full maneuverability is at your fingertips, allowing for precise handling whether you’re docking in tight marinas or navigating open waters. The advanced Seakeeper Gyro Stabilization System further enhances your ride, minimizing roll and providing a stable, comfortable experience even when the waves pick up. With this level of performance, the S 428 is ready to tackle long-range adventures, high-speed runs, and everything in between. Features and Specifications The Pursuit S 428…', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/26/34/2025-pursuit-s-428-power-9702634-976500558-0-090420250839-1.jpg?w=1920&h=267&t=1772315187000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/26/34/2025-pursuit-s-428-power-9702634-976500547-0-090420250839-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1772315187000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/26/34/2025-pursuit-s-428-power-9702634-976500566-0-090420250839-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1772315188000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/26/34/2025-pursuit-s-428-power-9702634-976500563-0-090420250839-4.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1772315188000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/26/34/2025-pursuit-s-428-p