 world of possibilities. Measuring an impressive 23.58 feet in length, this Ski & Wakeboard boat is engineered for both excitement and comfort. Its sleek profile, highlighted by Sepia Brown-Wakesetter Hull Side Graphics and an exterior color upgrade, ensures you’ll turn heads at every dock and marina. Built with Malibu’s renowned craftsmanship, this boat combines cutting-edge technology with premium materials, making it a standout choice for anyone seeking a new Malibu boat for sale. Performance At the heart of the Wakesetter 23 LSV is a powerful single engine boasting 460 horsepower. This robust engine delivers exhilarating acceleration, smooth cruising, and the torque needed to create massive wakes and waves for skiing, wakeboarding, and surfing. The advanced Zero Off GPS system ensures precision speed control, allowing riders to enjoy consistent, customizable experiences every time. Whether you’re carving through glassy water or powering through choppy conditions, the Wakesetter 23 LSV’s performance is engineered to impress. Features and Specifications The 2025 Malibu Wakesetter 23 LSV is packed with innovative features designed to enhance every aspect of your boating adventure. The Port Lower Rack - PTM Clampforce 30 offers secure storage for your…', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/87/66/2025-malibu-wakesetter-23-lsv-power-9858766-20250724170321707-1.jpg?w=1920&h=267&t=1774896346000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/87/66/2025-malibu-wakesetter-23-lsv-power-9858766-20250724170321752-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1772819169000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/87/66/2025-malibu-wakesetter-23-lsv-power-9858766-20250724170321726-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1772819161000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/87/66/2025-malibu-wakesetter-23-lsv-power-9858766-20250724170321853-4.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1772819165000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.co