. Its sleek, modern design is matched by robust engineering, ensuring a smooth and stable ride in a variety of conditions. As a new model, it offers the latest advancements in boating technology and comfort, making it a top contender for anyone searching for a center console boat for sale that delivers both excitement and reliability. Performance At the heart of the Axopar 25 Cross Top is a powerful 250-horsepower engine, engineered to provide exhilarating acceleration and impressive top speeds. This level of horsepower ensures that you can cruise effortlessly, whether you are navigating coastal waters, exploring inland lakes, or heading offshore for a day of adventure. The expertly crafted twin Ventera Pro Finish 15"x21" propellers further enhance performance, delivering smooth handling, responsive maneuverability, and optimal fuel efficiency. With this combination of power and precision, the Axopar 25 Cross Top is ready to take on any boating challenge with confidence. Features and Specifications The 2026 Axopar 25 Cross Top is loaded with premium features that set it apart from other center console boats for sale. Navigation is a breeze thanks to the twin chartplotter Simrad NSS4 12" displays, which are seamlessly integrated with…', '2026-04-01T17:58:41.846Z', '2026-04-01T17:58:41.846Z', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'ManufacturerPower Management and Systems - Bow thruster, Quick Power Management and Systems - Shore power system 110V w. 20Ah charger Power Management and Systems - Deck lights, 8 pcs Navigation option - Chartplotter Simrad NSX 12" Entertainment - Premium audio entertainment system, JL Audio Freshwater system - Fresh water system 32l incl. shower on aft deck Freshwater system - Seat base with top-loaded refrigerator and sink Freshwater system - Toilet electric fresh water flush, 25l septic tank Cushion Set - Sundeck cushions for front deck w. harbour cover, Cobre Optional equipment - Trim tabs Optional equipment - Echo sounder, thru hull