, NULL, NULL, 'Please contact Frank Grzeszczak Sr. at 9544947096', 'Frank Grzeszczak Sr.', '9544947096', 'MachineryMain Engines Engine Type: MTU 16V4000M73L Gearboxes for Main Engines: ZF 9350 Drive + Propeller Type: Shaft, out turning ME PT 9000 hr – QL3 - top end rebuild done dec 2024 at 9486 / current hrs 10252 ME STB 9000 hr – QL3 - top end rebuild done dec 2024 at 9607 / current hrs 10372 Speed (kts) Fuel Consumption (gal/hr) Range (RPM) 10.5 188 1000 12.5 334 1200 14.5 510 1400 20 1440 1950 Generators & Electricity Output: 200KW Generators: CAT C9 DITA X3 / CAT C4.4BITA Gen PT 12000hr- complete rebuild done dec 2022 @ 12791 / current hrs 20085 Gen Cen - complete rebuild in March 2025 / current hrs 12510 Gen STB 12000hr- complete rebuild done dec 2022 @ 11535 / current hrs 19816 Generator Fuel Consumption (gal/hour): 25L/H Shorepower: MAGNUS SP 200 250KVA Batteries Main Engine Starting: MASTERVOLT AGM 225AH X 12 Generator Starting: MASTERVOLT AGM 225AH X 12 Emergency: MASTERVOLT AGM 130AH X 4 Air Conditioning Type: HIEN & HOPMAN - CHILLED WATER Other Machinery Watermakers: HEM H30 DUPLEX MINI X2 Stabilizers: Naiad Dynamics Model 820 Bow Thruster: ZF TT 2001 FP Thruster systems (tunnel thruster fixed pitch) Steering system: JASTRAM Twin S2-21-1-35 Fuel Separator / Filtration: GEA W…', 'The Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors, to investigate such details as the buyer desires validated. This vessel is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal without notice.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Engine 1Engine Make:MTUEngine Model:16V 4000 M73LEngine Hours:10252Fuel Type:DieselEngine 2Engine Make:MTUEngine Model:16V 4000 M73LEngine Hours:10372Fuel Type:Diesel', 'MTU', '16V 4000 M73L', NULL, NULL, '10252 | 10372', NULL, NULL, 'Diesel', NULL, NULL, 'Speed & DistanceCruisin