est possible quality. She boasts one-of-a-kind artwork and offers a feast for the eyes. Able to accommodate up to 12 guests in five beautifully styled staterooms, She offers luxury and comfort on board. Private master stateroom with four additional staterooms, two twins and two doubles also accommodating guests in sophisticated style. Treat yourself to the sailing soul of 50M Project Troy/Synergy. She is in her final stages of construction and months from completion. Save yourself years of struggling and sail away this year!!!', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/62/76/2025-custom-global-saling-vessel-sail-9486276-20240729193743282-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=1920&h=267&t=1758675239000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/62/76/2025-custom-global-saling-vessel-sail-9486276-20240729193745408-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1758675200000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/62/76/2025-custom-global-saling-vessel-sail-9486276-20240729193752435-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1758675239000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/62/76/2025-custom-global-saling-vessel-sail-9486276-20240729193749740-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1758675239000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/62/76/2025-custom-global-saling-vessel-sail-9486276-20240729193741915-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1758675200000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/62/76/2025-custom-global-saling-vessel-sail-9486276-20240729194429986-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1758675200000&exact=&format=webp"]', 'Boat DetailsDescription50m SAILING SUPER YACHT Synergy Designed by Tim Saunders with the impressive super sailing performance as her central focus. A beautifully designed sailing yacht boasting both impeccable styling, comfort and unequaled elegance. The exterior is elegantly contemporary, yet rugged and aggressive. A stunning glass-paneling feature, which runs from the private aft-deck through the centerline of the yacht to the helm station, allowing sunlight to filter into the interior, illuminating the onboard living spaces. Indoors, She has been finished to the highest possible quality. She boasts one-of-a-kind artwork and offers a feast for the eyes. Able to accommodate up to 12 guests in five beautifully styled staterooms, She offers luxury and comfort on board. Private master stateroom with four additional staterooms, two twins and two doubles also accommodating guests in sophisticated style. Treat yourself to the sailing soul of 50M Project Troy/Synergy. She is in her final stages of construction and months from completion. Save yourself years of struggling and sail away this year!!!Show MoreContact InformationPlease contact Sakeena Hazuri-Mathis at 786-314-9441Other DetailsDisclaimerThe Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors, to investigate such details as the buyer desires validated. This vessel is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal without notice.Need more details?Ask the sellerFeaturesElectrical EquipmentShore Power Inlet:✓Generator:✓Inverter:✓ElectronicsDepthsounder:✓Radar:✓Log-Speedometer:✓Wind Speed and Direction:✓Computer:✓Repeater(s):✓TV Set:✓Navigation Cen…', '2026-04-01T02:56:42.871Z', '2026-04-01T02:56:42.871Z', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Please contact Sakeena Hazuri-Mathis at 786-314-9441', 'Sakeena Hazuri-Mathis', '786-314-9441', 'DisclaimerThe Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors, to investigate such details as the buyer desires validated. This vessel is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal without notice.', 'The 