d of effortless elegance: 5 Staterooms | 10 Guests | 5 Crew Full-Beam Owner’s Suite on the Main Deck with panoramic windows Expansive Flybridge with bar and dining area Jacuzzi on the bow Fold-Down Beach Club for seamless water access Carbon Fiber Construction for speed, stability, and efficiency Inside, Salvagni’s design invites you into a sophisticated yet welcoming atmosphere, where soft curves, curated textures, and custom furnishings elevate every detail. Outside, every deck is designed for living—whether entertaining on the flybridge, hosting cocktails on the foredeck, or retreating to the beach club at water’s edge. Powered by twin MTU engines and enhanced by Azimut’s Low Emission program, the 32M delivers both performance and sustainability, redefining what it means to cruise in luxury. The 2025 Azimut Grande 32 Metri is available for showings at the MarineMax Yacht Center in Pompano Beach, FL. Contact us today to schedule your private showing and experience the future of yachting.', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/21/84/2025-azimut-grande-32m-power-9712184-977693442-0-020520250925-7.png?w=400&h=267&t=1774994442000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/21/84/2025-azimut-grande-32m-power-9712184-977693447-0-020520250925-4.png?w=200&ratio=default&t=1774994449000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/21/84/2025-azimut-grande-32m-power-9712184-977693440-0-020520250925-2.png?w=200&ratio=default&t=1774994448000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/21/84/2025-azimut-grande-32m-power-9712184-977693437-0-020520250925-0.png?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1774994443000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/21/84/2025-azimut-grande-32m-power-9712184-977693439-0-020520250925-1.png?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1774994448000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/21/84/2025-azimut-grande-32m-power-9712184-977693428-0-020520250925-3.png?w=200&ratio=default&