atures a Master suite, a VIP cabin and 2 twin cabins, one of which includes an additional pullman bed and the other a convertible. FANCY’s large saloon, bathed in light through exceptionally large potholes, invites relaxation in a refined and intimate atmosphere. The small lounge offers a playful space for board games and film nights. FANCY’s specialised dining room is ideal for enjoying high-quality meals onboard. The crew have their own quarters and service entrance, which maintains privacy. On deck, FANCY has exceptional swimming platforms, as well as spacious relaxation and dining areas.', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/42/5/2023-nautor-swan-swan-108-sail-9644205-20241226085743650-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=400&h=267&t=1735232264000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/42/5/2023-nautor-swan-swan-108-sail-9644205-20241226085745465-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1735232266000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/42/5/2023-nautor-swan-swan-108-sail-9644205-20241226085747473-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1735232268000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/42/5/2023-nautor-swan-swan-108-sail-9644205-20241226085749492-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1735232270000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/42/5/2023-nautor-swan-swan-108-sail-9644205-20241226085751491-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1735232272000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/42/5/2023-nautor-swan-swan-108-sail-9644205-20241226085753497-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1735232274000&exact&format=webp"]', 'Boat DetailsDescriptionNautor Swan shipyard, with a high-end specification from a passionate owner, built the 108-foot sailing yacht FANCY in 2023. This innovative hull is the result of precision work, quality and attention to detail, offering outstanding performance, elegant design and luxurious comfort. This latest Swan maxi yacht has been designed and engineered for high speed sailing in all wind and sea conditions. She offers breath-taking sensations in comfortable and safe conditions, allowing for full enjoyment. FANCY can accommodate up to 9 people on board. Her interior features a Master suite, a VIP cabin and 2 twin cabins, one of which includes an additional pullman bed and the other a convertible. FANCY’s large saloon, bathed in light through exceptionally large potholes, invites relaxation in a refined and intimate atmosphere. The small lounge offers a playful space for board games and film nights. FANCY’s specialised dining room is ideal for enjoying high-quality meals onboard. The crew have their own quarters and service entrance, which maintains privacy. On deck, FANCY has exceptional swimming platforms, as well as spacious relaxation and dining areas.Show MoreOther DetailsAdditional Information- Latest high-performance yacht from the iconic Nautor Swan shipyard- Large central cockpit and sunbathing area - Impressive 11m² swim platform- Passionate and experienced crew, including a French gourmet chef- Starlink high-speed internet access- Telescopic keel, double rudder and full carbon rig- Northsails 3Di sail wardrobeNeed more details?Ask the sellerFeaturesElectronicsDepthsounder:✓Radar:✓Wind Speed and Direction:✓Computer:✓TV Set:✓Navigation Center:✓Plotter:✓Autopilot:✓Radio:✓Compass:✓GPS:✓Cockpit Speakers:✓VHF:✓Wi-Fi:✓AIS:✓Inside EquipmentStern Thruster:✓D…', '2026-04-01T01:52:48.710Z', '2026-04-01T01:52:48.710Z', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Additional Information- Latest high-performance yacht from the iconic Nautor Swan shipyard- Large central cockpit and sunbathing area - Impressive 11m² swim platform- Passionate and experienced crew, including a French gourmet chef- Starlink high-speed internet access- Telescopic keel, double rudder and full carbon rig- Northsails 3Di sail wardrobe', NULL, 'ElectronicsDepthsounder:✓Radar:✓Wind Speed and Direction:✓Computer:✓TV Set:✓Navigation Center:✓Plott