r tanks approx.500L Grey water tanks approx. 500L Fresh water tanks approx 2 x750L Fresh Water Level Sensor Holding tank sensor 24V DC Two (2) 24/12V DC Batteries Two (2) 24/12V DC Distribution Ten (10) 24/12V DC Control (Czone combination output module) One (1)…', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Engine 1Engine Type:InboardDrive Type:Direct DriveFuel Type:DieselEngine 2Engine Type:InboardFuel Type:Diesel', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Inboard', 'Direct Drive', 'Diesel', NULL, NULL, 'Speed & DistanceCruising Speed:10knDimensionsLength Overall:85ftMax Draft:3.61ftBeam:36.09ftMiscellaneousHull Material:FiberglassKeel Type:OtherTanksFresh Water Tank:Fuel Tank:Holding Tank:AccommodationsGuest Cabins:5', '10kn', NULL, NULL, '85ft', NULL, '3.61ft', NULL, '36.09ft', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Fiberglass', NULL, 'Other', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/71/43/2025-mcconaghy-mc86-sail-9887143-20250728210032830-1.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1774929956000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/71/43/2025-mcconaghy-mc86-sail-9887143-20250728210032839-2.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1774929954000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/71/43/2025-mcconaghy-mc86-sail-9887143-20250728210032847-3.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1774929958000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/71/43/2025-mcconaghy-mc86-sail-9887143-20250728210032854-4.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1774929959000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/71/43/2025-mcconaghy-mc86-sail-9887143-20250728210032861-5.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1774929956000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/71/43/2025-mcconaghy-mc86-sail-9887143-20250728210032868-6.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1774929956000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/71/43/2025-mcconaghy-mc86-sail-9887143-20250728210032875-7.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1774929954000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.