olo adventures and outings with friends or family. Key Features: 14’4” aluminum jon boat for shallow water and versatile use Open deck layout for maximum casting and gear space Lightweight yet durable aluminum construction Stable and easy-to-handle for rivers, lakes, and backwaters Optional seating and storage for convenience Ideal for fishing, hunting, or recreational boating The Lund Jon 1448 is the perfect small boat for anglers and outdoor enthusiasts seeking rugged reliability, simplicity, and versatility. Sale price does not include $699 dealer fee. Length Overall: 164 in. (4200 mm) Beam: 70 in. (1.8 m) Dry Weight: 260 lb. (117.9 kg.) Max Person Capacity: 4 Max Carry Load: 831 lb. (376.9 kg.)', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/85/74/2025-lund-jon-1448-power-9928574-20251215113227820-1.jpg?w=400&h=267&t=1774993042000&exact&format=webp"]', 'Boat DetailsDescription2025 Lund Jon 1448, Lund Jon 1448 The Lund Jon 1448 is a rugged, versatile aluminum jon boat designed for anglers, hunters, and outdoor enthusiasts who demand durability and performance in a compact package. Lightweight yet sturdy, this 14’4” boat is ideal for shallow waters, rivers, lakes, and backwaters. Its open, functional layout provides plenty of room for fishing, gear, or hunting equipment. Built with Lund’s reputation for quality craftsmanship and durable materials, the Jon 1448 delivers a stable, reliable ride and low-maintenance performance, making it perfect for both solo adventures and outings with friends or family. Key Features: 14’4” aluminum jon boat for shallow water and versatile use Open deck layout for maximum casting and gear space Lightweight yet durable aluminum construction Stable and easy-to-handle for rivers, lakes, and backwaters Optional seating and storage for convenience Ideal for fishing, hunting, or recreational boating The Lund Jon 1448 is the perfect small boat for anglers and outdoor enthusiasts seeking rugged reliability, simplicity, and ver