ckpit, integrated bow seating, and intuitive helm layout, the 211 Valanti is a perfect choice for boating enthusiasts seeking versatility without compromise. At Boater’s World Bradenton, our focus on pre-owned boat sales in Southwest Florida means you’re backed by our expertise and commitment to quality. Each vessel on our lot undergoes a comprehensive inspection — and this Regal is no exception. From its well-cared-for upholstery to its clean gelcoat and reliable inboard powerplant, this 1998 Regal 211 Valanti represents exceptional value in the used bowrider market. Features you’ll love: Spacious bow seating with dual-level comfort Full cockpit layout with adjustable helm seating Swim platform with easy water access Reliable inboard motor for smooth acceleration and handling Ample storage for gear, coolers, and water toys Whether you’re exploring local waters, fishing with friends, or enjoying family days at anchor, this used bowrider offers roomy comfort and classic Regal performance. Stop by Boater’s World Bradenton to see this 1998 Regal 211 Valanti in person — our friendly sales team is here to help you find the right boat to fit your lifestyle and budget.', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/60/16/1998-regal-211-power-9866016-985608117-0-090720250415-1.jpg?w=400&h=267&t=1774993001000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/60/16/1998-regal-211-power-9866016-985608118-0-090720250415-2.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1774993003000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/60/16/1998-regal-211-power-9866016-985608119-0-090720250415-3.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1774993002000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/60/16/1998-regal-211-power-9866016-985608120-0-090720250415-4.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1774993002000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/60/16/1998-regal-211-power-9866016-985608121-0-090720250415-5.jpg?w=200&ratio=default&t=1774993002000&exact&format=webp",