e legacy of the legendary BENETEAU Wizz, the First 14 reproduces the exhilarating world of fast planning dinghies. Light, accessible, and easy to handle, the boat is perhaps best described as essentially fun, and the quality of her build simplifies maintenance and guarantees worry-free ownership.', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/84/74/2021-beneteau-first-14-sail-9648474-20250205234150112-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1738827711000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/84/74/2021-beneteau-first-14-sail-9648474-20250205234610315-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1738827971000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/84/74/2021-beneteau-first-14-sail-9648474-20250205234708597-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1738828029000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/84/74/2021-beneteau-first-14-sail-9648474-20250205234744022-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1738828065000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/84/74/2021-beneteau-first-14-sail-9648474-20250205234902335-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1738828143000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/84/74/2021-beneteau-first-14-sail-9648474-20260310212800895-1.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1773204183000&exact=&format=webp"]', 'Boat DetailsDescription THESE BOATS CAN EASILY BE SHIPPED CHEAPLY ANYWHERE GLOBALY IN A SHIPPING CONTAINER We have a fleet of 5 matching F-14''s for sale in Ocean Marina Pattaya. having been lightly used for 3 years we are now ready to present them for sale individually or as a fleet to their next owners. Great fun to sail and providing a great performance either crewed as single or double handed. Ask us about our try before you buy offer on these boats!!! We are so confident that you will love these boats we are offering you to go for a test sail before you decide to buy. Building on the legacy of the legendary BENETEAU Wizz, the First 14 reproduces the exhilarating world of fast planning dinghies. Light, accessible, and easy to handle, the boat is perhaps best described as essentially fun, and the quality of her build simplifies maintenance and guarantees worry-free ownership.Show MoreContact InformationPlease contact Howard Prime at +66 (0) 86 277 3360Other DetailsAdditional InformationAt Primus Marine we offer all types of new and boats for sale from small tenders right up to over 130 feet. We have 3 offices in Thailand, being Bangkok, Pattaya and Phuket and also 1 in Singapore. Please reach out to us to organise a meeting to discuss your wants and needs for your next boat and we can also provide expert information on the cruising grounds and relevant port authorities throughout Asia. All of our offices are located close to international airports, therefore we can easily pick you up if flying in to view a boat from abroad or elsewhere locally in SE Asia. Primus Marine offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surve…', '2026-04-01T15:09:54.217Z', '2026-04-01T15:09:54.217Z', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Please contact Howard Prime at +66 (0) 86 277 3360', 'Howard Prime', NULL, 'Additional InformationAt Primus Marine we offer all types of new and boats for sale from small tenders right up to over 130 feet. We have 3 offices in Thailand, being Bangkok, Pattaya and Phuket and also 1 in Singapore. Please reach out to us to organise a meeting to discuss your wants and needs for your next boat and we can also provide expert information on the cruising grounds and relevant port authorities throughout Asia. All of our offices are located close to international airports, therefore we can easily pick you up if flying in to view a boat from abroad or elsewhere locally in SE Asia. Primus Marine offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors, to investigate such details as the buyer desires validated. This vessel is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal without notice.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'DimensionsLength Overall:14.08ftBeam:5.58ftWeightsDry Weight:148LbMiscellaneousSeating Capacity:3Hull Material:FiberglassHull Shape:FlatKeel Type:CenterboardTanksFresh Water Tank:Fuel Tank:Holding Tank:', NULL, NULL, NULL, '14.08ft', NULL, NULL, NULL, '5.58ft', '148Lb', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Fiberglass', 'Flat', 'Centerboard', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/0/45/7860045_20210422151441867_1_XLARGE.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1736240372000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/0/45/7860045_20210422151435900_1_XLARGE.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1736240372000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/0/45/7860045_20210422151438074_1_XLARGE.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1736240372000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/0/45/7860045_20210422151440066_1_XLARGE.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1736240372000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/0/45/7860045_20210422151444111_1_XLARGE.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1736240372000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/84/74/2021-beneteau-first-14-sail-9648474-20250205234150112-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1738827711000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/84/74/2021-beneteau-first-14-sail-9648474-20250205234610315-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1738827971000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/84/74/2021-beneteau-first-14-sail-9648474-20250205234708597-1_XLARGE.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1738828029000&exact&format=webp"]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Pattaya, Thailand, US', 'Pat