. The FLICKA is perfect for both leisurely sails and spirited day trips, making it an excellent choice for sailing enthusiasts. Embrace the joy of sailing with this delightful classic vessel, where timeless craftsmanship meets dependable performance.', 'dealer', 'sale', '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/85/19/1969-greenwich-24-sail-9988519-20251022121454283-1.jpg?w=1920&h=267&t=1761161398000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/85/19/1969-greenwich-24-sail-9988519-20251022120821219-1.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1761160516000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/85/19/1969-greenwich-24-sail-9988519-20251022120822259-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1761161006000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/85/19/1969-greenwich-24-sail-9988519-20251022120908289-1.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1761161053000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/85/19/1969-greenwich-24-sail-9988519-20251022120909406-2.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1761161052000&exact=&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/85/19/1969-greenwich-24-sail-9988519-20251022120909982-3.jpg?w=1920&ratio=default&t=1761161052000&exact=&format=webp"]', 'Boat DetailsDescriptionIntroducing the FLICKA, a charming 1969 Allied Greenwich 24 sloop that combines classic design with modern performance. With an overall length of 24.25 feet, this vessel features a fiberglass hull and a full keel, ensuring stability and a smooth sailing experience. Powered by a 6 hp Yamaha outboard engine, the FLICKA is ready for your next adventure on the water. This boat''s thoughtful design includes essential features for enjoyable outings. While it offers ample space for relaxation, it is also equipped with practical amenities to enhance your time on board. The FLICKA is perfect for both leisurely sails and spirited day trips, making it an excellent choice for sailing enthusiasts. Embrace the joy of sailing with this delightful classic vessel, where timeless craftsmanship meets dependable performance.Show MoreContact InformationPlease contact Bob Vaughan at 207 326 4411Other DetailsAdditional Information- Self-baling cockpit - cabin sleeps four - outboard stows neatly in lazarette - 25# plow anchor on bow pulpit - compass - life jackets - NO trailer The Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors, to investigate such details as the buyer desires validated. This vessel is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal without notice.Need more details?Ask the sellerFeaturesElectronicsCompass:✓VHF:✓Inside EquipmentMarine Head:marine pottiOutside EquipmentTeak Cockpit:cockpit coamings and toerailsTiller:✓Cockpit Cushions:five (5) cabin cushionsSailsBattened Mainsail:Pope with four (4) battens, NEWFurling Genoa:Harken roller furler, 2019Want more features?Ask the seller…', '2026-04-01T03:59:06.758Z', '2026-04-01T03:59:06.758Z', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Please contact Bob Vaughan at 207 326 4411', 'Bob Vaughan', '207 326 4411', 'Additional Information- Self-baling cockpit - cabin sleeps four - outboard stows neatly in lazarette - 25# plow anchor on bow pulpit - compass - life jackets - NO trailer The Company offers the details of this vessel in good faith but cannot guarantee or warrant the accuracy of this information nor warrant the condition of the vessel. A buyer should instruct his agents, or his surveyors, to investigate such details as the buyer desires validated. This vessel is offered subject to prior sale, price change, or withdrawal without notice.', NULL, 'ElectronicsCompass:✓VHF:✓Inside EquipmentMarine Head:marine pottiOutside EquipmentTeak Cockpit:cockpit coamings and toerailsTiller:✓Cockpit Cushions:five (5) cabin cushionsSailsBattened Mainsail:Pope with four (4) battens, NEWFurling Genoa:Harken roller furler, 2019', NULL, 'Compass | VHF', 'Marine Head: marine potti', 'Teak Cockpit: cockpit coamings and toerails | Tiller | Cockpit Cushions: five (5) cabin cushions | Sails | Battened Mainsail: Pope with four (4) battens, NEWFurling Genoa: Harken roller furler, 2019', NULL, 'Engine Make:YamahaEngine Year:2018Total Power:6hpEngine Type:OutboardFuel Type:Gas', 'Yamaha', NULL, '2018', '6hp', NULL, 'Outboard', NULL, 'Gas', NULL, NULL, 'DimensionsLength Overall:24.25ftMax Draft:3ftBeam:7.25ftLength at Waterline:17.42ftMiscellaneousHull Material:FiberglassKeel Type:Full KeelTanksFresh Water Tank:Fuel Tank:Holding Tank:', NULL, NULL, NULL, '24.25ft', NULL, '3ft', NULL, '7.25ftLength at Waterline:17.42ft', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Fiberglass', NULL, 'Full Keel', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '["https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/85/19/1969-greenwich-24-sail-9988519-20251022121454283-1.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1761161398000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/85/19/1969-greenwich-24-sail-9988519-20251022120821219-1.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1761160516000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/85/19/1969-greenwich-24-sail-9988519-20251022120822259-2.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1761161006000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/85/19/1969-greenwich-24-sail-9988519-20251022120908289-1.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1761161053000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/85/19/1969-greenwich-24-sail-9988519-20251022120909406-2.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1761161052000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/85/19/1969-greenwich-24-sail-9988519-20251022120909982-3.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1761161052000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/85/19/1969-allied-greenwich-24-sail-9988519-20251212061214899-1.jpg?w=1028&ratio=default&t=1765549642000&exact&format=webp","https://images.boatsgroup.com/resize/1/85/19/1969-allied-greenwich-24-sail-9988519-20251212061457717-1.jpg?w=1028&rati